generated as baselines.'=>'返回正在监控的品牌搜索查询列表，包括当前启用的搜索查询和自动生成的基线。','Brand UUID. Obtain from get-ai-visibility-overview or get-ai-visibility-brand-insights.'=>'品牌 UUID。从 get-ai-visibility-overview 或 get-ai-visibility-brand-insights 获取。','Get AI Visibility overview'=>'获取 AI 可见性概述','Returns the site-level AI Visibility summary and the full list of tracked brands with their current scores, ranks, sentiment, and analysis status.'=>'返回站点级 AI 可见性摘要和跟踪品牌的完整列表及其当前分数、排名、情绪和分析状态。','Pass true to bypass the 12-hour dashboard cache and return a stale-flagged response. Use the REST endpoint to trigger a fresh upstream fetch.'=>'传递 true 以绕过 12 小时仪表板缓存并返回过时标记的响应。使用 REST 端点触发新的上游获取。','Filter brands by name or URL (case-insensitive substring match).'=>'按名称或 URL 过滤品牌（不区分大小写的子字符串匹配）。','AI Visibility'=>'AI 可见性','Abilities to retrieve AI brand visibility data tracked by Rank Math.'=>'能够检索由 Rank Math 跟踪的 AI 品牌可见度数据。','Get top keywords'=>'获取热门关键字','Returns the top-performing keywords by clicks from Google Search Console, with impressions, CTR, and average position for the selected date range.'=>'根据 Google Search Console 的点击次数返回效果最好的关键字，以及所选日期范围内的展示次数、点击率和平均排名。','Date range for which to fetch keyword data.'=>'获取关键字数据的日期范围。','Maximum number of keywords to return.'=>'要返回的关键字的最大数量。','The search query keyword.'=>'搜索查询关键字。','Total clicks from Google Search Console.'=>'总点击次数来自 Google Search Console。','Total impressions from Google Search Console.'=>'来自 Google Search Console 的总展示次数。','Click-through rate as a percentage (0–100).'=>'点击率百分比 (0–100)。','Average position in Google Search results.'=>'Google 搜索结果中的平均排名。','Position trend vs. the previous period. Provided by Rank Math PRO for tracked keywords.'=>'与上一时期相比的排名趋势。由 Rank Math PRO 为跟踪的关键字提供。','Whether this keyword is tracked in Rank Math PRO Rank Tracker.'=>'此关键字是否在 Rank Math PRO 排名跟踪器中跟踪。','Pages on your site that rank for this keyword. Provided by Rank Math PRO.'=>'您网站上为此关键字排名的页面。由 Rank Math PRO 提供。','WordPress post ID.'=>'WordPress 帖子 ID。','Post title.'=>'帖子标题。','Relative URL path of the page.'=>'页面的相对 URL 路径。','Whether Google Search Console is connected.'=>'是否已连接 Google Search Console。','Analytics'=>'分析','Abilities to query Google Search Console and analytics data.'=>'查询 Google Search Console 和分析数据的能力。','Analyze post content'=>'分析帖子内容','Gathers the raw content, metadata, and list of on-page SEO tests for a saved post so an AI agent can run Rank Math\'s full on-page analysis itself, since the scoring engine only runs client-side. Use tests_to_run and content together with kb_link (the scoring rubric for all 24 tests) to evaluate each test and produce a per-test score, status, and fix message.'=>'收集原始内容、元数据和页面 SEO 列表测试已保存的帖子，以便 AI 代理可以自行运行 Rank Math 的完整页面分析，因为评分引擎仅运行客户端。将tests_to_run和内容与kb_link（所有24个测试的评分标准）一起使用来评估每个测试并生成每个测试的分数、状态和修复消息。','ID of the post to analyze.'=>'要分析的帖子的ID。','Optional focus keyword to analyze against, overriding the post\'s saved focus keyword.'=>'要分析的可选焦点关键字，覆盖帖子已保存的焦点关键字。','No post found with the given ID, or the post status is not supported.'=>'没有找到具有给定ID的帖子，或者帖子状态不受支持。','Evaluate each test ID in tests_to_run against the fields in content, using kb_link as the scoring rubric for how each test is scored. Return a per-test breakdown with score, max_score, status (pass/fail), and a message with a specific fix. For the contentHasTOC test, when suggesting a fix or drafting content, tell the user to insert the Rank Math Table of Contents block (block name rank-math/toc-block, available in the block inserter as "Table of Contents") right after the intro, instead of a manual list of links — it auto-generates from the post headings.'=>'评估每个测试ID test_to_run 针对内容中的字段，使用 kb_link 作为每个测试如何评分的评分标准。返回每个测试的详细信息，包括分数、最大分数、状态（通过/失败）以及包含特定修复的消息。对于 contentHasTOC 测试，当建议修复或起草内容时，告诉用户在介绍之后插入 Rank Math 目录块（块名称 rank-math/toc-block，在块插入器中可用作“目录”），而不是手动链接列表 - 它会从帖子标题自动生成。','Get SEO scores'=>'获取 SEO 分数','Returns SEO scores and grades for posts. Before running, ask the user which posts they want to review: posts needing improvement (bad score), posts with no focus keyword, unscored posts, or simply the most recently modified posts. Use this to surface which posts need SEO attention without needing to know post IDs in advance.'=>'返回帖子的 SEO 分数和等级。在运行之前，询问用户他们想要查看哪些帖子：需要改进的帖子（分数不好）、没有焦点关键字的帖子、未评分的帖子或只是最近修改的帖子。使用此功能可以显示哪些帖子需要 SEO 关注，而无需提前知道帖子 ID。','Number of recently modified posts to retrieve. Defaults to 10, maximum 100.'=>'要检索的最近修改的帖子数量。默认为 10，最大为 100。','Post type to filter by (e.g. "post", "page"). Defaults to all public post types.'=>'要过滤的帖子类型（例如“帖子”、“页面”）。默认为所有公共帖子类型。','Ask the user which posts they want to review before running this ability. Available options: "bad" (score ≤ 50, needs improvement), "good" (score 51–80, ok), "great" (score > 80), "empty-fk" (no focus keyword set), "unscored" (never analyzed). If the user does not specify, omit this parameter to return the most recently modified posts.'=>'在运行此功能之前询问用户他们想要查看哪些帖子。可用选项：“差”（分数 ≤ 50，需要改进）、“好”（分数 51-80，还可以）、“很棒”（分数 > 80）、“empty-fk”（未设置焦点关键字）、“unscored”（从未分析过）。如果用户未指定，则省略此参数以返回最近修改的帖子。','Not available'=>'不可用','Good'=>'良好','OK'=>'确定','Needs improvement'=>'需要改进','Content Analysis'=>'内容分析','Abilities to retrieve on-page SEO analysis scores for posts.'=>'能够检索帖子的页面 SEO 分析分数。','Get link report'=>'获取链接报告','Returns a site-wide link health report: total internal and external links, post counts with no internal or external links, and — on Rank Math PRO — broken links, redirects, nofollow counts, and HTTP status distribution from the Link Genius audit.'=>'返回站点范围的链接健康状况报告：内部和外部链接总数、无链接的帖子数内部或外部链接，以及 — 在 Rank Math PRO 上 — 来自 Link Genius 审核的损坏链接、重定向、nofollow 计数和 HTTP 状态分布。','Get post links'=>'获取帖子链接','Returns a paginated list of internal and external links stored for a given post, including the URL, link type, and target post details for internal links.'=>'返回为给定帖子存储的内部和外部链接的分页列表，包括内部链接的 URL、链接类型和目标帖子详细信息。','ID of the post whose links to retrieve.'=>'要检索其链接的帖子的 ID。','Upgrade to Rank Math PRO to unlock broken link detection, redirect chain analysis, and HTTP status distribution from the Link Genius audit.'=>'升级到 Rank Math PRO 以解锁损坏的链接Link Genius 审核中的检测、重定向链分析和 HTTP 状态分布。','Link Genius'=>'Link Genius','Abilities to retrieve and analyse internal and external link data for posts.'=>'能够检索和分析帖子的内部和外部链接数据。','Get post SEO metadata'=>'获取帖子 SEO 元数据','Returns the full SEO metadata for a post: title, description, focus keyword, robots settings, canonical URL, Open Graph and Twitter overrides, and the current SEO score.'=>'返回帖子的完整 SEO 元数据：标题、描述、焦点关键字、机器人设置、规范 URL、开放图谱和 Twitter 覆盖以及当前 SEO 分数。','The ID of the post to retrieve SEO metadata for.'=>'帖子的 ID检索 SEO 元数据。','Post SEO'=>'帖子 SEO','Abilities to read and manage per-post SEO metadata.'=>'能够读取和管理每个帖子 SEO 元数据。','Get post schema'=>'获取帖子结构化数据','Returns the schema markup attached to a post and the schema types available on this install. Use this after rank-math/get-post-seo-meta to check what schema is already set and what types are supported before making a recommendation. If the schema type you want to recommend is not in available_types.types and upgrade_message is present, show upgrade_message verbatim to the user and do not suggest adding the schema type directly.'=>'返回附加到帖子的结构化数据标记以及此安装中可用的结构化数据类型。在rank-math/get-post-seo-meta之后使用此命令来检查已设置的结构化数据以及支持的类型，然后再提出建议。如果您要推荐的结构化数据类型不在 available_types.types 中并且存在upgrade_message，则向用户逐字显示upgrade_message，并且不建议直接添加结构化数据类型。','The ID of the post to retrieve schema markup for.'=>'要检索其结构化数据标记的帖子的 ID。','When true (default), includes the schema types available on this install. Always pass true when evaluating which schema to add.'=>'如果为 true（默认），则包括此安装中可用的结构化数据类型。在评估要添加的结构化数据时始终传递 true。','Invalid post ID.'=>'帖子 ID 无效。','This schema type requires Rank Math PRO. Upgrade at rankmath.com/pro to unlock Movie, Dataset, Fact Check, and custom schema types.'=>'此结构化数据类型需要 Rank Math PRO。在rankmath.com/pro 升级以解锁电影、数据集、事实检查和自定义结构化数据类型。','Schema'=>'结构化数据','Abilities to read and manage schema markup attached to posts.'=>'能够读取和管理附加到帖子的结构化数据标记。','The provided URL is not valid.'=>'提供的 URL 无效。','Competitor URL analysis requires Rank Math PRO. Upgrade at %s'=>'竞争对手 URL 分析需要 Rank Math PRO。在 %s 升级','Audit site SEO'=>'审核网站 SEO','Runs Rank Math\'s site-wide SEO audit and returns a structured score plus per-test findings with fix hints. Combines local checks with the remote rankmath.com API tests.'=>'运行 Rank Math 的网站范围 SEO 审核并返回结构化分数以及带有修复提示的每次测试结果。将本地检查与远程rankmath.com API 测试相结合。','Re-run the audit. Defaults to true (always fresh when called by an AI host).'=>'重新运行审核。默认为 true（由 AI 主机调用时始终保持最新）。','Optional URL to audit. Defaults to this site\'s home URL. When provided, only remote API tests run (local checks are site-wide).'=>'要审核的可选 URL。默认为本网站的主页 URL。如果提供，则仅运行远程 API 测试（本地检查是站点范围内的）。','No automatic fix is available for test "%s". Use the fix_text guidance to resolve it manually.'=>'没有可用于测试“%s”的自动修复。使用 fix_text 指南手动解决该问题。','Site visibility set to public. Search engines can now index your site.'=>'站点可见性设置为公开。搜索引擎现在可以为您的网站编制索引。','Permalink structure is already set to /%postname%/.'=>'永久链接结构已设置为 /%postname%/。','Permalink structure set to /%postname%/ and rewrite rules flushed.'=>'永久链接结构设置为 /%postname%/ 并刷新重写规则。','A "value" input is required to set the site tagline. Provide a short, unique description of your site.'=>'需要输入“值”来设置网站标语。提供您网站的简短、独特的描述。','The provided tagline is the default WordPress value. Please supply a unique tagline.'=>'提供的标语是默认的 WordPress 值。请提供唯一的标语。','Site tagline updated to: "%s".'=>'站点标语已更新为："%s"。','Sitemap module enabled. Your XML sitemap is now active.'=>'站点地图模块已启用。您的 XML 站点地图现已激活。','Schema / rich snippet module enabled.'=>'结构化数据/丰富代码段模块已启用。','Global robots setting updated to allow indexing. Run a fresh audit to confirm the remote API test passes.'=>'全局机器人设置已更新以允许建立索引。运行新的审核以确认远程 API 测试通过。','OpenGraph output is always enabled in Rank Math. If this test is failing, the remote audit API may need a fallback Open Graph image. Set one at Rank Math → Titles & Meta → Global Meta → Open Graph T