ater.'=>'该服务暂时不可用。请稍后重试。','Unauthorized request. The client credentials are invalid.'=>'未经授权的请求。客户端凭据无效。','No results found for the given query. Please modify your request and try again'=>'未找到给定查询的结果。请修改您的请求并重试','Insufficient results to complete the request. Please refine your query or reduce the requirements.'=>'结果不足，无法完成请求。请优化您的查询或减少要求。','User wallet not found.'=>'未找到用户钱包。','Rank Math SEO: Getting error "%1$s" while creating table <code>%2$s</code>. Please contact your server administrator to fix this issue.'=>'排名数学 SEO：创建表 <code>%2$s</code> 时出现错误 "%1$s"。请联系您的服务器管理员来解决此问题。','There was an issue scheduling the async action required for Analytics; if the problem persists, please contact our support team.'=>'安排 Analytics 所需的异步操作时出现问题；如果问题仍然存在，请联系我们的支持团队。','There was an issue scheduling a single action required for Analytics; if the problem persists, please contact our support team.'=>'安排 Analytics 所需的单个操作时出现问题；如果问题仍然存在，请联系我们的支持团队。','There was an issue scheduling the recurring action required for Analytics; if the problem persists, please contact our support team.'=>'安排 Analytics 所需的重复操作时出现问题；如果问题仍然存在，请联系我们的支持团队。','There was an issue unscheduling a background action related to Analytics; if the problem persists, please contact our support team.'=>'取消安排与 Analytics 相关的后台操作时出现问题；如果问题仍然存在，请联系我们的支持团队。','WooCommerce Product'=>'WooCommerce 产品','No file selected for upload.'=>'未选择上传文件。','Items per page'=>'每页项目数','404 Monitor'=>'404 监控','Records the URLs on which visitors & search engines run into 404 Errors. You can also turn on Redirections to redirect the error causing URLs to other URLs.'=>'记录访问者和搜索引擎遇到 404 错误的 URL。您还可以打开重定向，将导致错误的 URL 重定向到其他 URL。','Dominate the search results for the local audiences by optimizing your website for Local SEO and it also helps you to acquire the Knowledge Graph.'=>'通过针对本地 SEO 优化您的网站，主导本地受众的搜索结果，并且还可以帮助您获取知识图。','Redirections'=>'重定向','Redirect non-existent content easily with 301 and 302 status code. This can help improve your site ranking. Also supports many other response codes.'=>'使用 301 和 302 状态代码轻松重定向不存在的内容。这可以帮助提高您的网站排名。还支持许多其他响应代码。','Schema (Structured Data)'=>'结构化数据（结构化数据）','Enable support for the structured data, which adds Schema code in your website, resulting in rich search results, better CTR and more traffic.'=>'启用对结构化数据的支持，这会在您的网站中添加结构化数据代码，从而获得丰富的搜索结果、更好的点击率和更多流量。','Sitemap'=>'站点地图','Enable Rank Math\'s sitemap feature, which helps search engines intelligently crawl your website\'s content. It also supports hreflang tag.'=>'启用Rank Math的站点地图功能，这有助于搜索引擎智能地抓取您网站的内容。它还支持 hreflang 标签。','Link Counter'=>'链接计数器','Counts the total number of internal, external links, to and from links inside your posts. You can also see the same count in the Posts List Page.'=>'计算帖子内的内部、外部链接以及往返链接的总数。您还可以在帖子列表页面中看到相同的计数。','An advanced internal linking tool that analyzes your posts, tracks link data, highlights opportunities, and offers detailed report.'=>'高级内部链接工具，可分析您的帖子、跟踪链接数据、突出显示机会并提供详细报告。','This module is available in the PRO version.'=>'此模块在 PRO 版本中提供。','Image SEO'=>'图像 SEO','Advanced Image SEO options to supercharge your website. Automate the task of adding the ALT and Title tags to your images on the fly.'=>'高级图像 SEO 选项可增强您的网站。自动执行将 ALT 和标题标签动态添加到图像的任务。','Instant Indexing'=>'即时索引','Directly notify search engines like Bing & Yandex using the %s when pages are added, updated and removed, or submit URLs manually.'=>'在添加、更新和删除页面时，使用 %s 直接通知 Bing 和 Yandex 等搜索引擎，或手动提交 URL。','IndexNow API'=>'IndexNow API','Content AI'=>'内容 AI','Get sophisticated AI suggestions for related Keywords, Questions & Links to include in the SEO meta & Content Area. Supports 80+ Countries.'=>'获取相关关键字、问题和链接的复杂 AI 建议，以包含在 SEO 元和内容区域中。支持 80 多个国家/地区。','LLMS Txt'=>'LLMS Txt','Serve a custom llms.txt file to guide AI models with posts, terms, and most important content on your website.'=>'提供自定义 llms.txt 文件，通过您网站上的帖子、术语和最重要的内容来指导 AI 模型。','News Sitemap'=>'新闻站点地图','Create a News Sitemap for your news-related content. You only need a News sitemap if you plan on posting news-related content on your website.'=>'为您的新闻相关内容创建新闻站点地图。如果您计划在网站上发布新闻相关内容，则仅需要新闻站点地图。','Video Sitemap'=>'视频站点地图','For your video content, a Video Sitemap is a recommended step for better rankings and inclusion in the Video search.'=>'对于您的视频内容，建议使用视频站点地图，以便在视频搜索中获得更好的排名和收录。','Podcast'=>'播客','Make your podcasts discoverable via Google Podcasts, Apple Podcasts, and similar services with Podcast RSS feed and Schema Markup generated by Rank Math.'=>'使用播客 RSS 提要和 Rank Math 生成的结构化数据标记，让您的播客可通过 Google 播客、Apple 播客和类似服务被发现。','Track your brand\'s AI search visibility. Monitor brand mentions, citations, & sentiment, and discover opportunities to grow your AI visibility.'=>'跟踪您品牌的 AI 搜索可见性。监控品牌提及、引用和情绪，并发现提高 AI 知名度的机会。','Role Manager'=>'角色管理器','The Role Manager allows you to use WordPress roles to control which of your site users can have edit or view access to Rank Math\'s settings.'=>'角色管理器允许您使用 WordPress 角色来控制哪些网站用户可以编辑或查看 Rank Math 设置的访问权限。','Connect Rank Math with Google Search Console to see the most important information from Google directly in your WordPress dashboard.'=>'将 Rank Math 与 Google Search Console 连接，直接在 WordPress 仪表板中查看来自 Google 的最重要信息。','SEO Analyzer'=>'SEO 分析器','Let Rank Math analyze your website and your website\'s content using 28+ different tests to provide tailor-made SEO Analysis to you.'=>'让 Rank Math 分析您的网站使用超过 28 种不同的测试来分析您网站的内容，为您提供量身定制的 SEO 分析。','Robots Txt'=>'Robots Txt','Version Control'=>'版本控制','Database Tools'=>'数据库工具','Status'=>'状态','AMP'=>'AMP','Install %s to make Rank Math work with Accelerated Mobile Pages. Rank Math automatically adds required meta tags in all the AMP pages.'=>'安装 %s 以使 Rank Math 与 Accelerated Mobile Pages 配合使用。 Rank Math 会自动在所有 AMP 页面中添加所需的元标记。','AMP plugin'=>'AMP 插件','bbPress'=>'bbPress','Add proper Meta tags to your bbPress forum posts, categories, profiles, etc. Get more options to take control of what search engines see and how they see it.'=>'向您的 bbPress 论坛帖子、类别、个人资料等添加适当的元标记。获取更多选项来控制搜索引擎看到的内容以及查看方式。','Please activate bbPress plugin to use this module.'=>'请激活 bbPress 插件以使用此模块。','BuddyPress'=>'BuddyPress','Enable the BuddyPress module for Rank Math SEO to make your BuddyPress forum SEO friendly by adding proper meta tags to all forum pages.'=>'为 Rank Math SEO 启用 BuddyPress 模块通过向所有论坛页面添加适当的元标记，使您的 BuddyPress 论坛 SEO 友好。','Please activate BuddyPress plugin to use this module.'=>'请激活 BuddyPress 插件以使用此模块。','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Optimize WooCommerce Pages for Search Engines by adding required metadata and Product Schema which will make your site stand out in the SERPs.'=>'通过添加所需的元数据和产品结构化数据来优化搜索引擎的 WooCommerce 页面，这将使您的网站在 SERP 中脱颖而出。','Please activate WooCommerce plugin to use this module.'=>'请激活 WooCommerce 插件以使用此模块。','ACF'=>'ACF','ACF support helps Rank Math SEO read and analyze content written in the Advanced Custom Fields. If your theme uses ACF, you should enable this option.'=>'ACF 支持可帮助 Rank Math SEO 读取和分析高级自定义字段中写入的内容。如果您的主题使用 ACF，则应启用此选项。','Please activate ACF plugin to use this module.'=>'请激活 ACF 插件以使用此模块。','Google Web Stories'=>'Google 网络故事','Make any Story created with the Web Stories WordPress plugin SEO-Ready with automatic support for Schema and Meta tags.'=>'使用网络故事 WordPress 插件创建的任何故事都已做好 SEO 准备，并自动支持结构化数据和元标记。','Please activate Web Stories plugin to use this module.'=>'请激活网络故事插件以使用此模块。','You cant access this page.'=>'您无法访问此模块页。','Free'=>'免费','NEW!'=>'新功能！','More powerful options are available in the PRO version.'=>'PRO 版本中提供了更强大的选项。','PRO options are enabled.'=>'PRO 选项已启用。','Take SEO to the Next Level!'=>'将 SEO 提升到新的水平！','Unlimited personal websites'=>'无限个人网站','Free 15-Day Content AI Trial'=>'免费 15 天内容 AI 试用','Track 500 Keywords'=>'跟踪 500 个关键字','24/7 Support'=>'24/7支持','Buy'=>'购买','Settings'=>'设置','%d log(s) deleted.'=>'%d 条日志已删除。','Log cleared - %d items deleted.'=>'日志已清除 - %d 项已删除。','Overview'=>'概述','Screen Content'=>'屏幕内容','Available Actions'=>'可用操作','Bulk Actions'=>'批量操作','Are you sure you wish to delete all 404 error logs?'=>'您确定要