ou can reorder the list by clicking on the column headings. '=>'您可以通过单击列标题对列表重新排序。','Search'=>'搜索','If you have hundreds of 404 errors, your error log might increase quickly. Only choose this option if you have a very few 404s and are unable to replicate the 404 error on a particular URL from your end.'=>'如果您有数百个 404 错误，您的错误日志可能会快速增加。仅当您的 404 错误很少并且无法从您的端复制特定 URL 上的 404 错误时，才选择此选项。','Mode'=>'模式','The Simple mode only logs URI and access time, while the Advanced mode creates detailed logs including additional information such as the Referer URL.'=>'简单模式仅记录 URI 和访问时间，而高级模式创建详细日志，包括引用网址 URL 等其他信息。','Simple'=>'简单','Advanced'=>'高级','Log Limit'=>'日志限制','Sets the max number of rows in a log. Set to 0 to disable the limit.'=>'设置日志中的最大行数日志。设置为 0 可禁用限制。','Exclude Paths'=>'排除路径','Enter URIs or keywords you wish to prevent from getting logged by the 404 monitor.'=>'输入您希望阻止 404 监视器记录的 URI 或关键字。','Add another'=>'添加另一个','Remove'=>'删除','Ignore Query Parameters'=>'忽略查询参数','Turn ON to ignore all query parameters (the part after a question mark in a URL) when logging 404 errors.'=>'打开以在记录 404 时忽略所有查询参数（URL 中问号后面的部分）错误。','New!'=>'新！','AI Visibility %s'=>'AI 可见性 %s','Rank Math account not connected. Please connect your account and try again.'=>'排名数学帐户未连接。请连接您的帐户，然后重试。','AI Visibility API returned an unexpected status: %d'=>'AI Visibility API 返回意外状态：%d','AI Visibility API returned an invalid response.'=>'AI Visibility API 返回无效响应。','Brand UUID.'=>'品牌 UUID。','Force a refresh from the AI Visibility API.'=>'从 AI Visibility API 强制刷新。','Filter brands by name or URL.'=>'按名称或 URL 过滤品牌。','Brand website URL or domain.'=>'品牌网站 URL 或域。','ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code (e.g. "US", "HU").'=>'ISO 3166-1 alpha-2国家/地区代码（例如 "US"、"HU"）。','Query UUID.'=>'查询 UUID。','Whether the query is enabled for analysis.'=>'是否启用查询进行分析。','No fields to update.'=>'没有要更新的字段。','Could not start the checkout session. Please try again.'=>'无法启动结账会话。请重试。','Your AI Visibility trial has been activated.'=>'您的 AI Visibility 试用版已激活。',