r website in the Rank Math 404 Monitor.'=>'404 错误日志是否失控？使用此选项可清除 Rank Math 404 监视器中您的网站生成的所有 404 日志。','Are you sure you want to delete the 404 log? This action is irreversible.'=>'您确定要删除 404 日志吗？此操作不可逆转。','Re-create Missing Database Tables'=>'重新创建丢失的数据库表','Check if required tables exist and create them if not.'=>'检查所需的表是否存在，如果不存在则创建它们。','Re-create Tables'=>'重新创建表','Fix Analytics table collations'=>'修复 Analytics 表排序规则','In some cases, the Analytics database tables or columns don\'t match with each other, which can cause database errors. This tool can fix that issue.'=>'在某些情况下，Analytics 数据库表或列彼此不匹配，这可能会导致数据库错误。此工具可以解决该问题。','Fix Collations'=>'修复排序规则','Yoast Block Converter'=>'Yoast 块转换器','Convert FAQ, HowTo, & Table of Contents Blocks created using Yoast. Use this option to easily move your previous blocks into Rank Math.'=>'转换使用 Yoast 创建的常见问题解答、操作方法和目录块。使用此选项可以轻松地将以前的块移动到 Rank Math 中。','Are you sure you want to convert Yoast blocks into Rank Math blocks? This action is irreversible.'=>'您确定要将 Yoast 块转换为 Rank Math 块吗？此操作不可逆转。','Convert Blocks'=>'转换块','AIOSEO Block Converter'=>'AIOSEO 块转换器','Convert TOC block created using AIOSEO. Use this option to easily move your previous blocks into Rank Math.'=>'转换使用 AIOSEO 创建的 TOC 块。使用此选项可以轻松地将您以前的块移至 Rank Math 中。','Are you sure you want to convert AIOSEO blocks into Rank Math blocks? This action is irreversible.'=>'您确定要将 AIOSEO 块转换为 Rank Math 块吗？此操作是不可逆的。','Delete Internal Links Data'=>'删除内部链接数据','In some instances, the internal links data might show an inflated number or no number at all. Deleting the internal links data might fix the issue.'=>'在某些情况下，内部链接数据可能会显示夸大的数字或根本没有数字。删除内部链接数据可能会解决该问题。','Are you sure you want to delete Internal Links Data? This action is irreversible.'=>'您确定要删除内部链接数据吗？此操作不可逆转。','Delete Internal Links'=>'删除内部链接','Delete Redirections Rules'=>'删除重定向规则','Getting a redirection loop or need a fresh start? Delete all the redirections using this tool. Note: This process is irreversible and will delete ALL your redirection rules.'=>'出现重定向循环或需要重新开始？使用此工具删除所有重定向。注意：此过程不可逆，并且将删除您的所有重定向规则。','Are you sure you want to delete all the Redirection Rules? This action is irreversible.'=>'您确定要删除所有重定向规则吗？此操作不可逆转。','Delete Redirections'=>'删除重定向','Update SEO Scores'=>'更新 SEO 分数','This tool will calculate the SEO score for the posts/pages that have a Focus Keyword set. Note: This process may take some time and the browser tab must be kept open while it is running.'=>'此工具将计算设置了焦点关键字的帖子/页面的 SEO 分数。注意：此过程可能需要一些时间，并且运行时浏览器选项卡必须保持打开状态。','Recalculate Scores'=>'重新计算分数','Purge Analytics Cache'=>'清除分析缓存','Clear analytics cache to re-calculate all the stats again.'=>'清除分析缓存以再次重新计算所有统计数据。','Clear Cache'=>'清除缓存','Missing some posts/pages in the Analytics data? Clear the index and build a new one for more accurate stats.'=>'分析数据中缺少某些帖子/页面？清除索引并构建新索引以获得更准确的统计数据。','To properly rebuild Analytics posts in secondary languages, please disable the %1$s when using a different domain per language.'=>'要正确重建第二语言的 Analytics 帖子，请在每种语言使用不同域时禁用 %1$s。','Make themes work multilingual option in WPML settings'=>'在 WPML 设置中使主题支持多语言选项','Rebuild Index for Analytics'=>'重建分析索引','Rebuild Index'=>'重建索引','Images'=>'图像','SEO options related to featured images and media appearing in your post content. %s.'=>'与帖子内容中出现的特色图像和媒体相关的 SEO 选项。 %s。','Add missing ALT attributes'=>'添加缺少的 ALT 属性','Add <code>alt</code> attributes for <code>images</code> without <code>alt</code> attributes automatically. The attribute is dynamically applied when the content is displayed, and the stored content is not changed.'=>'自动为没有 <code>alt</code> 属性的<code>图像</code>添加 <code>alt</code> 属性。显示内容时会动态应用该属性，并且存储的内容不会更改。','Alt attribute format'=>'Alt 属性格式','Format used for the new <code>alt</code> attribute values.'=>'用于新 <code>alt</code> 属性值的格式。','Add missing TITLE attributes'=>'添加缺少的 TITLE 属性','Add <code>TITLE</code> attribute for all <code>images</code> without a <code>TITLE</code> attribute automatically. The attribute is dynamically applied when the content is 