n successfully restored.'=>'重定向成功恢复。','%d redirection(s) successfully deleted.'=>'%d 个重定向成功已删除。','Warning: you have more than %d active redirections. Exporting them to your .htaccess file may cause performance issues.'=>'警告：您有超过 %d 个活动重定向。将它们导出到 .htaccess 文件可能会导致性能问题。','Export to .htaccess'=>'导出到 .htaccess','Export to Nginx config file'=>'导出到 Nginx 配置文件','Export'=>'导出','Redirection successfully deleted.'=>'重定向成功删除。','Can\'t update redirection.'=>'无法更新重定向。','Redirection updated successfully.'=>'重定向更新成功。','New redirection created.'=>'创建新重定向。','Invalid regex pattern: %s'=>'无效的正则表达式模式: %s','Redirection Count'=>'重定向计数','Total number of Redirections created in the Rank Math.'=>'排名数学中创建的重定向总数。','Redirection Hits'=>'重定向点击次数','Total number of hits received by all the Redirections.'=>'所有重定向收到的点击总数。','Create and edit redirections'=>'创建和编辑重定向','Manage Redirections'=>'管理重定向','Redirection Settings'=>'重定向设置','&raquo; Redirect this page'=>'&raquo;重定向此页面','Redirect the current URL'=>'重定向当前 URL','No redirections found in Trash.'=>'垃圾箱中未找到重定向。','No redirections added yet. <a href="#" class="rank-math-add-new-redirection">Add New Redirection</a>'=>'尚未添加重定向。 <a href="#" class="rank-math-add-new-redirection">添加新重定向</a>','Show more'=>'显示更多','Hide details'=>'隐藏详细信息','Hide'=>'隐藏','Restore'=>'恢复','Delete Permanently'=>'删除永久','Edit'=>'编辑','Deactivate'=>'停用','Activate'=>'激活','Trash'=>'废纸篓','From'=>'从','To'=>'到','Type'=>'类型','Created'=>'创建','Last Accessed'=>'上次访问','Move to Trash'=>'移至废纸篓','Active'=>'活动','Inactive'=>'非活动','Empty Trash'=>'清空废纸篓','SEO Notice: you just changed the slug of a %1$s and Rank Math has automatically created a redirection. You can edit the redirection by <a href="%2$s">clicking here</a>.'=>'SEO 注意：您刚刚更改了 %1$s 的 slug，Rank Math 已自动创建重定向。您可以通过<a href="%2$s">单击此处</a>编辑重定向。','<strong>SEO Notice:</strong> A previously published %1$s has been moved to trash. You may redirect <code>%2$s</code> to <a href="%3$s">a new url</a>.'=>'<strong>SEO 通知</strong>：之前发布的 %1$s 已移至回收站。您可以将 <code>%2$s</code> 重定向到<a href="%3$s">新网址</a>。','Rank Math SEO Redirection Debugger'=>'排名数学 SEO 重定向调试器','Redirection Debugger'=>'重定向调试器','Redirecting from '=>'从',' To '=>'重定向到','Redirecting in %s seconds...'=>'在 %s 秒内重定向...','Stop Redirection'=>'停止重定向','Continue redirecting'=>'继续重定向','Manage This Redirection'=>'管理此重定向','or'=>'或','Manage All Redirections'=>'管理所有重定向','<strong>Note:</strong> This interstitial page is displayed only to administrators. Site visitors are redirected without delay.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>此插页式页面仅向管理员显示。网站访问者会立即重定向。','Served from cache'=>'从缓存提供服务','<strong>Edit</strong> redirection details: from/to URLs and the redirection type.'=>'<strong>编辑</strong>重定向详细信息：来源/目标 URL 和重定向类型。','<strong>Activate/Deactivate</strong> redirections. Deactivated redirections do not take effect on your site.'=>'<strong>激活/停用</strong>重定向。停用的重定向不会在您的网站上生效。','<strong>Delete</strong> permanently removes the redirection.'=>'<strong>删除</strong>会永久删除重定向。','You can also activate, deactivate, or delete multiple items at once using the Bulk Actions dropdown.'=>'您还可以使用“批量操作”下拉列表一次激活、停用或删除多个项目。','Here you can set up custom redirections. It is important to choose the right type of redirection.'=>'您可以在此处设置自定义重定向。选择正确的重定向类型非常重要。','301 redirections are <em>permanent</em>. The old URL will be removed in search engines and replaced by the new one, passing on SearchRank and other SEO scores. Browsers may also store the new URL in cache and redirect to it even after the redirection is deleted from the list here.'=>'301 重定向是<em>永久</em>。旧的 URL 将在搜索引擎中删除并被新的 URL 取代，从而传递 SearchRank 和其他 SEO 分数。即使从此处的列表中删除了重定向，浏览器也可能会将新的 URL 存储在缓存中并重定向到该 URL。','Using a 302 <em>temporary</em> redirection is useful when you want to test a new page for client feedback temporarily without affecting the SEO scores of the original page.'=>'当您想要暂时测试新页面以获取客户反馈而不影响原始页面的 SEO 分数时，使用 302 临时重定向非常有用。','Redirections can be exported to your .htaccess file for faster redirections, in SEO > Settings > Import/Export.'=>'可以将重定向导出到 .htaccess 文件，以实现更快的重定向，请在 SEO > 设置 >导入/导出。','Debug Redirections'=>'调试重定向','Display the Debug Console instead of being redirected. Administrators only.'=>'显示调试控制台而不是被重定向。仅限管理员。','Fallback Behavior'=>'回退行为','If nothing similar is found, this behavior will be applied. <strong>Note</strong>: If the requested URL ends with <code>/login</code>, <code>/admin</code>, or <code>/dashboard</code>, WordPress will automatically redirect to respective locations within the WordPress admin area.'=>'如果没有发现类似的情况，将应用此行为。 <strong>注意</strong>：如果请求的 URL 以 <code>/login</code>、<code>/admin</code> 或 <code>/dashboard</code> 结尾，WordPress 将自动重定向到 WordPress 管理区域内的相应位置。','Default 404'=>'默认 404','Redirect to Homepage'=>'重定向到主页','Custom Redirection'=>'自定义重定向','Custom Url '=>'自定义 URL','Redirection Type'=>'重定向类型','Auto Post Redirect'=>'自动帖子重定向','Extend the functionality of WordPress by creating redirects in our plugin when you change the slug of a post, page, category or a CPT. You can modify the redirection further according to your needs.'=>'当您更改帖子、页面、类别或 CPT 的 slug 时，通过在我们的插件中创建重定向来扩展 WordPress 的功能。您可以根据需要进一步修改重定向。','Edit robots.txt'=>'编辑 robots.txt','Edit your robots.txt file to control what bots see. %s.'=>'编辑 robots.txt 文件以控制机器人看到的内容。 %s。','Leave the field empty to let WordPress handle the contents dynamically. If an actual robots.txt file is present in the root folder of your site, this option won\'t take effect and you have to edit the file directly, or delete it and then edit from here.'=>'将该字段留空，让 WordPress 动态处理内容。如果您网站的根文件夹中存在实际的 robots.txt 文件，则此选项不会生效，您必须直接编辑该文件，或者删除该文件，然后从此处进行编辑。','Contents are locked because a robots.txt file is present in the root folder.'=>'由于根文件夹中存在 robots.txt 文件，内容被锁定。','Rank Math could not detect if a robots.txt file exists or not because of a filesystem issue. The file contents entered here may not be applied.'=>'由于文件系统问题，Rank Math 无法检测 robots.txt 文件是否存在。此处输入的文件内容可能无法应用。','robots.txt file is not writable.'=>'robots.txt 文件不可写。','<strong>Warning:</strong> your site\'s search engine visibility is set to Hidden in <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Settings &gt; Reading</a>. This means that the changes you make here will not take effect. Set the search engine visibility to Public to be able to change the robots.txt content.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>您网站的搜索引擎可见性已在<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">设置 > 中设置为隐藏。阅读</a>。这意味着您在此处所做的更改将不会生效。将搜索引擎可见性设置为公开，以便能够更改 robots.txt 内容。','Test and edit your live robots.txt file with our <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Robots.txt Tester</a>.'=>'使用我们的<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Robots.txt 测试器</a>测试和编辑您的实时 robots.txt 文件。','Titles & Meta Settings'=>'标题和元设置','Sitemap Settings'=>'站点地图设置','404 Monitor Log'=>'404 监控日志','Link Builder'=>'链接生成器','Site-Wide Analysis'=>'全站分析','On-Page Analysis'=>'页面分析','On-Page General Settings'=>'页面常规设置','On-Page Advanced Settings'=>'页面高级设置','On-Page Schema Settings'=>'页面结构化数据设置','On-Page Social Settings'=>'页面社交设置','Top Admin Bar'=>'顶部管理栏','Blocks'=>'块','Take control over the default settings available for Rank Math Blocks.'=>'控制排名数学块的默认设置。','%d day'=>'%d 天','%d hour'=>'%d 小时','%d minute'=>'%d 分钟','%1$s and %2$s'=>'%1$s 和 %2$s','%1$s, %2$s and %3$s'=>'%1$s、%2$s 和 %3$s','Total Time:'=>'总计时间：','Table of Contents Title'=>'目录标题','Enter the default title to use for the Table of Contents block.'=>'输入目录块使用的默认标题。','Table of Contents'=>'目录','Table of Contents List style'=>'目录列表样式','Select the default list style for the Table of Contents block.'=>'选择目录块的默认列表样式。','Numbered'=>'编号','Unordered'=>'无序','Table of Contents Exclude Headings'=>'目录排除标题','Choose the headings to exclude from the Table of Contents block.'=>'选择标题从目录块中排除。','Heading H1'=>'标题 H1','Heading H2'=>'标题 H2','Heading H3'=>'标题 H3','Heading H4'=>'标题 H4','Heading H5'=>'标题 H5','Heading H6'=>'标题 H6','No schema found.'=>'未找到模式。','Days'=>'天数','Opening Time'=>'开放时间','Closing Time'=>'结束时间','Editor\'s Rating:'=>'编辑评级：','Author'=>'作者','Edition'=>'版本','Name'=>'名称','Url'=>'网址','ISBN'=>'ISBN','Date Published'=>'发布日期','Format'=>'格式','Course Provider'=>'课程提供商','Course Provider Name'=>'课程提供商名称','Course Provider URL'=>'课程提供商 URL','Course Mode'=>'课程模式','Course Workload'=>'课程工作量','Start Date'=>'开始日期','End Date'=>'结束日期','Duration'=>'持续时间','Repeat Count'=>'重复次数','Repeat Frequency'=>'重复频率','Course Type'=>'课程类型','Course Currency'=>'课程货币','Course Price'=>'课程价格','Online + Offline'=>'线上+线下','Event Type'=>'活动类型','Event Attendance Mode'=>'活动出席方式','Event Status'=>'活动状态','Venue Name'=>'场地名称','Venue URL'=>'场地网址','Online Event URL'=>'线上活动网址','Performer'=>'表演者','Performer Name'=>'表演者姓名','Performer URL'=>'表演者网址','Ticket URL'=>'门票网址','Entry Price'=>'入场价格','Currency'=>'货币','Availability'=>'可用性','Availability Starts'=>'可用性开始','Stock Inventory'=>'库存','Salary'=>'工资','Salary Currency'=>'工资货币','Payroll'=>'工资','Date Posted'=>'发布日期','Expiry Posted'=>'发布到期','Unpublish when expired'=>'过期取消发布','Employment Type '=>'雇佣类型','Hiring Organization '=>'招聘组织','Organization URL'=>'组织 URL','Organization Logo'=>'组织徽标','Location'=>'位置','Gender'=>'性别','Job Title'=>'职位','Product SKU'=>'产品SKU','Product Brand'=>'产品品牌','Product Currency'=>'产品货币','Product Price'=>'产品价格','Price Valid Until'=>'价格有效期至','Product In-Stock'=>'产品库存','Cuisine'=>'美食','Keywords'=>'关键字','Recipe Yield'=>'食谱产量','Calories'=>'卡路里','Preparation Time'=>'准备时间','Cooking Time'=>'烹饪时间','Total Time'=>'总时间','Recipe Video Name'=>'菜谱视频名称','Recipe Video Description'=>'菜谱视频描述','Recipe Video Thumbnail'=>'菜谱视频缩略图','Recipe Ingredients'=>'菜谱配料','Recipe Instructions'=>'菜谱说明','Serves Cuisine'=>'份数美食','Menu URL'=>'菜单URL','Service Type'=>'服务类型','Price'=>'价格','Price Currency'=>'价格货币','Operating System'=>'操作系统','Application Category'=>'应用程序类别','Site-wide analysis'=>'站点范围分析','Analyze this Page'=>'分析此页面','SEO Analysis for this page'=>'此页面的 SEO 分析','Rank Math auto-update option is enabled on your site.'=>'您的网站上启用了排名数学自动更新选项。','HTTP %d error.'=>'HTTP %d 错误。','Unexpected API response.'=>'意外的 API 响应。','(No Title)'=>'(否标题）','(No Description)'=>'（无描述）','Site Tagline'=>'网站标语','Your theme may display the Site Tagline, and it can also be used in SEO titles &amp; descriptions. Set it to something unique. You can change it by navigating to <a href="%s">Settings &gt; General</a>.'=>'您的主题可以显示网站标语，它也可以用于 SEO 标题和主题。描述。将其设置为独特的东西。您可以通过导航至<a href="%s">设置 > 来更改它。一般</a>。','Most WordPress themes place your site\'s tagline in a prominent position (inside header tags near the top of the page).  Using the right tagline can give your site an SEO boost.'=>'大多数 WordPress 主题将网站的标语放在显着位置（靠近页面顶部的标题标签内）。  使用正确的标语可以为您的网站带来 SEO 提升。','Unfortunately, the standard WordPress tagline is "Just Another WordPress site."  That\'s pretty sloppy looking, and it does nothing for your SEO.  In fact, it\'s actually a security risk - it makes it easy for hackers with a WordPress exploit to locate your site with an automated search.'=>'不幸的是，标准的 WordPress 标语是“只是另一个 WordPress 网站。”这看起来非常草率，而且对您的 SEO 毫无帮助。  事实上，这实际上是一个安全风险 - 它使利用 WordPress 漏洞的黑客可以轻松地通过自动搜索找到您的网站。','Changing your tagline is very easy.  Just head on over to <a target="_blank" href="%1$s">Settings - General</a> in WordPress\'s admin menu (on the left), or click on the link in this sentence.'=>'更改您的标语非常容易。  只需前往 WordPress 管理菜单（左侧）中的<a target="_blank" href="%1$s">设置 - 常规</a>，或点击这句话中的链接即可。','The tagline is the second option.  Choose a tagline that summarizes your site in a few words.  The tagline is also a good place to use your main keyword.'=>'标语是第二个选项。  选择一个用几句话概括您的网站的标语。  标语也是使用主关键字的好地方。','Confirm custom tagline is set for your site'=>'确认为您的网站设置了自定义标语','Blog Public'=>'博客公开','Your site may not be visible to search engine.'=>'您的网站可能对搜索引擎不可见。','You must %1$sgo to your Reading Settings%2$s and uncheck the box for Search Engine Visibility.'=>'您必须%1$s转到您的阅读设置%2$s并取消选中搜索引擎可见性复选框。','Check your site\'s visibility to search engines'=>'检查您的网站对搜索引擎的可见性','Permalink Structure'=>'永久链接结构','For the best SEO results, use a custom permalink structure, preferably one that includes the post title (<code>%%postname%%</code>). You can change it by navigating to <a href="%s">Settings &gt; Permalinks</a>'=>'为了获得最佳 SEO 结果，请使用自定义永久链接结构，最好是包含帖子标题 (<code>%%postname%%</code>) 的结构。您可以通过导航至<a href="%s">设置 > 来更改它。固定链接</a>','The standard permalink structure is pretty ugly - WordPress generates offputting URLs like: http://www.yoursite.com/?p=99'=>'标准的永久链接结构非常丑陋 - WordPress 生成令人讨厌的 URL，例如：http://www.yoursite.com/?p=99','It\'s not very kind on the eyes, and it does nothing for your site\'s SEO.  In fact, it can hurt it - Google\'s bot is quite cautious about crawling pages that look auto-generated.'=>'这对眼睛不太友好，而且对网站的 SEO 没有任何帮助。  事实上，它可能会伤害它 - Google 的机器人对于抓取看起来自动生成的页面非常谨慎。','Fortunately, it\'s very easy to fix.  Just hop on over to <a target="_blank" href="%1$s">Settings - Permalinks</a>.  Then chose the "Post Name" option.'=>'幸运的是，它很容易修复。  只需跳到<a target="_blank" href="%1$s">设置 - 固定链接</a>即可。  然后选择“帖子名称”选项。','This option will replace the "?p=99" part of the URL with the post\'s title, like this: http://www.yoursite.com/my-amazing-post-title/'=>'此选项将用帖子标题替换 URL 的“?p=99”部分，如下所示：http://www.yoursite.com/my-amazing-post-title/','This looks nice for readers - and it gets your keywords into the URL (keywords in the URL is a ranking factor).'=>'这对读者来说看起来不错 - 并且它将您的关键字放入 URL（URL 中的关键字是排名因素）。','Check your site for SEO-friendly permalink structure'=>'检查您的网站是否有 SEO 友好的永久链接结构','Focus Keywords'=>'焦点关键字','Setting focus keywords for your posts allows Rank Math to analyse the content.'=>'为您的帖子设置焦点关键字可以让 Rank Math 分析内容。','Rank Math allows you to set a focus keyword for every post and page you write - the option is in the "Meta Box", which appears under the text editor in the screen where you write and edit content.'=>'Rank Math 允许您为您编写的每个帖子和页面设置焦点关键字 - 该选项位于“元框”中，该框出现在您编写和编辑内容的屏幕中的文本编辑器下方。','Rank Math uses these focus keywords to analyze your on-page content.  It can tell if you\'ve done a good job of optimizing your text to rank for these keywords.'=>'Rank Math 使用这些焦点关键字来分析您的页面内容。  它可以判断您是否在优化文本以对这些关键字进行排名方面做得很好。','Of course, if you don\'t give Rank Math a focus keyword to work with, it can\'t give you any useful feedback.'=>'当然，如果您没有为 Rank Math 提供可使用的焦点关键字，它无法为您提供任何有用的反馈。','Fixing this issue is easy - just edit the post, and set a Focus Keyword.  Then follow Rank Math\'s analysis to improve your rankings.'=>'解决此问题很简单 - 只需编辑帖子，然后设置焦点关键字即可。  然后按照 Rank Math 的分析来提高您的排名。','Confirm focus keywords are set for all your posts'=>'确认您的所有帖子都设置了焦点关键字','Post Titles Missing Focus Keywords'=>'帖子标题缺少焦点关键字','Make sure the focus keywords you set for the posts appear in their titles.'=>'确保您为帖子设置的焦点关键字出现在其标题中。','HTML Page Titles play a large role in Google\'s ranking algorithm.  When you add a Focus Keyword to a post or page, Rank Math will check to see that you used the keyword in the title.  If it finds any posts or pages that are missing the keyword in the title, it will tell you here.'=>'HTML 页面标题在 Google 排名算法中发挥着重要作用。  当您将焦点关键字添加到帖子或页面时，排名数学将检查您是否在标题中使用了该关键字。  如果它发现标题中缺少关键字的任何帖子或页面，它会在此处告诉您。','Fixing the issue is simple - just edit the post/page and add the focus keyword(s) to the title.'=>'解决问题很简单 - 只需编辑帖子/页面并将焦点关键字添加到标题即可。','Verify the presence of focus keywords in your post titles'=>'验证帖子标题中是否存在焦点关键字','Register at Google Search Console and verificate your site by adding the code to <a href="%1$s">Settings &gt; Verificate Tools</a>, then navigate to <a href="%2$s">Settings &gt; Search Console</a> to authenticate and link your site.'=>'在 Google Search Console 注册并通过将代码添加到<a href="%1$s">设置 > 来验证您的网站验证工具</a>，然后导航至<a href="%2$s">设置 > Search Console</a> 用于验证和链接您的网站。','Google\'s Search Console is a vital source of information concerning your rankings and click-through rates.  Rank Math can import this data, so you don\'t have to log into your Google account to get the data you need.'=>'Google 的 Search Console 是有关您的排名和点击率的重要信息来源。  Rank Math 可以导入这些数据，因此您无需登录 Google 帐户即可获取所需的数据。','You can integrate the Google Search Console with Rank math in the <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Search Console tab</a>. of Rank Math\'s General Settings menu.'=>'您可以将 Google Search Console 与 <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Search Console 标签</a>中的 Rank Math 集成。','Read <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">this article</a> for detailed instructions on setting up your Google Webmaster account and getting Rank Math to work with the Google Search Console.'=>'阅读<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">本文</a>，了解有关设置 Google 网站站长帐户以及让 Rank Math 与 Google Search Console 配合使用的详细说明。','Confirm if Rank Math is connected to Search Console'=>'确认 Rank Math 是否已连接到 Search Console','Sitemaps'=>'站点地图','XML sitemaps are a special type of text file that tells search engines about the structure of your site. They\'re a list of all the resources (pages and files) you would like the search engine to index. You can assign different priorities, so certain pages will be crawled first. Before XML sitemaps, search engines were limited to indexing the content they could find by following links. That\'s still an important feature for search engine spiders, but XML sitemaps have made it easier for content creators and search engines to collaborate.'=>'XML 站点地图是一种特殊类型的文本文件，可以向搜索引擎告知以下信息您网站的结构。它们是您希望搜索引擎索引的所有资源（页面和文件）的列表。您可以分配不同的优先级，以便首先抓取某些页面。在 XML 站点地图出现之前，搜索引擎仅限于对它们可以通过以下链接找到的内容进行索引。这仍然是搜索引擎蜘蛛的一个重要功能，但 XML 站点地图使内容创建者和搜索引擎的协作变得更加容易。','If you don\'t have an XML sitemap, the best option is to install a plugin that creates sitemaps for you. That way you\'ll know the sitemap will always be up-to-date. Plugins can also automatically ping the search engines when the XML file is updated. The Rank Math WordPress plugin gives you complete control over your site\'s XML sitemaps. You can control the settings for each page as you write or edit it, and Rank Math will ping Google as soon as you submit your edits. This results in fast crawls and indexing.'=>'如果您没有 XML 站点地图，最好的选择是安装一个为您创建站点地图的插件。这样您就会知道站点地图将始终是最新的。当 XML 文件更新时，插件还可以自动 ping 搜索引擎。 Rank Math WordPress 插件使您可以完全控制站点的 XML 站点地图。您可以在编写或编辑页面时控制每个页面的设置，一旦您提交编辑内容，Rank Math 就会立即 ping Google。这样可以实现快速抓取和索引。','Check the presence of sitemaps on your website'=>'检查您的网站上是否存在站点地图','Automatic Updates'=>'自动更新','Enable automatic updates to ensure you are always using the latest version of Rank Math.'=>'启用自动更新以确保您始终使用最新版本的 Rank Math。','Verify auto-updates are enabled for Rank Math'=>'验证 Rank Math 的自动更新已启用','Site wide plugins auto-update option is disabled on your site.'=>'您的网站上禁用了全站范围插件自动更新选项。','Automatic updates are not enabled on your site. %s'=>'您的网站上未启用自动更新。 %s','Enable Auto Updates'=>'启用自动更新','You have not entered a tagline yet. It is a good idea to choose one. %1$sYou can fix this in the customizer%2$s.'=>'您尚未输入标语。选择一个是个好主意。 %1$s您可以在自定义程序%2$s中修复此问题。','Your Site Tagline is set to the default value <em>Just another WordPress site</em>.'=>'您的网站标语设置为默认值<em>只是另一个 WordPress 网站</em>。','Your Site Tagline is set to a custom value.'=>'您的网站标语设置为自定义值。','Permalinks are set to the default value. <em>Pretty permalinks</em> are disabled. '=>'永久链接设置为默认值。 <em>漂亮的永久链接</em>已被禁用。','Permalinks are set to a custom structure but the post titles do not appear in the permalinks.'=>'永久链接设置为自定义结构，但帖子标题不会出现在永久链接中。','Post permalink structure is set to %s.'=>'帖子永久链接结构设置为 %s。','Google Search Console has been linked.'=>'Google Search Console 已链接。','You have not linked Google Search Console yet.'=>'您尚未链接 Google Search Console。','Could not check Focus Keywords in posts - the post meta table exceeds the size limit.'=>'无法检查帖子中的焦点关键字 - 帖子元表超出大小限制。','All published posts have focus keywords set.'=>'所有发布的帖子都有焦点关键字设置。','There are %s with no focus keyword set.'=>'有 %s 个帖子未设置焦点关键字。','Focus keywords appear in the titles of published posts where it is set.'=>'焦点关键字出现在已设置的已发布帖子的标题中。','+%d More...'=>'+%d 更多...','There are %s published posts where the primary focus keyword does not appear in the post title.'=>'有 %s 个已发布帖子的主要焦点关键字未出现在帖子标题中。','Your site has one or more sitemaps.'=>'您的网站有一个或多个站点地图。','No sitemaps found.'=>'未找到站点地图。','Attention: Search Engines can\'t see your website.'=>'注意：搜索引擎看不到你的网站。','Navigate to %1$sSettings > Reading%2$s and turn off this option: "Discourage search engines from indexing this site".'=>'导航到 %1$s 设置 > 读取%2$s 并关闭此选项：\\“阻止搜索引擎对此站点建立索引\\”。','Your site is accessible by search engine.'=>'您的站点可由搜索引擎访问。','General'=>'常规','This tab contains General settings related to the XML sitemaps.'=>'此选项卡包含与 XML 站点地图相关的常规设置。','Your sitemap index can be found here: %s'=>'您可以在此处找到站点地图索引：%s','This tab contains settings related to the HTML sitemap.'=>'此选项卡包含与 HTML 相关的设置站点地图。','Set the sitemap options for author archive pages. %s.'=>'设置作者存档页面的站点地图选项。 %s。','attachments'=>'附件','your product pages'=>'您的产品页面','single %s'=>'单个 %s','Change Sitemap settings of %1$s. %2$s.'=>'更改 %1$s 的站点地图设置。 %2$s。','Sitemap URL: %s'=>'站点地图 URL：%s','Please note that this will add the attachment page URLs to the sitemap, not direct image URLs.'=>'请注意，这会将附件页面 URL 添加到站点地图，而不是直接图像 URL。','Taxonomies:'=>'分类法：','your product %s pages'=>'您的产品 %s 页面','%s archives'=>'%s 存档','Exclude this attachment from sitemap'=>'从站点地图中排除此附件','Since you are using an NGINX server, you may need to add the following code to your %s <strong>if your Sitemap pages are not loading</strong>. If you are unsure how to do it, please contact your hosting provider.'=>'由于您使用的是 NGINX 服务器，因此您可能需要添加<strong>如果您的站点地图页面未加载</strong>，请将以下代码发送给您的 %s。如果您不确定如何操作，请联系您的托管提供商。','configuration file'=>'配置文件','Click here to see the code.'=>'单击此处查看代码。','I already added'=>'我已经添加了','Rank Math has detected a new post type: %1$s. You may want to check the settings of the <a href="%2$s">Titles &amp; Meta page</a> and <a href="%3$s">the Sitemap</a>.'=>'Rank Math 检测到新的帖子类型：%1$s。您可能需要检查<a href="%2$s">标题和标题的设置元页面</a>和<a href="%3$s">站点地图</a>。','Rank Math has detected new post types: %1$s. You may want to check the settings of the <a href="%2$s">Titles &amp; Meta page</a> and <a href="%3$s">the Sitemap</a>.'=>'Rank Math 检测到新的帖子类型：%1$s。您可能需要检查<a href="%2$s">标题和标题的设置元页面</a>和<a href="%3$s">站点地图</a>。','XML Sitemap %1$s %2$s'=>'XML 站点地图 %1$s %2$s','Locations Sitemap %1$s %2$s'=>'位置站点地图 %1$s %2$s','Include in Sitemap'=>'包含在站点地图中','Include author archives in the XML sitemap.'=>'在 XML 站点地图中包含作者档案。','Include in HTML Sitemap'=>'包含在 HTML 站点地图中','Include author archives in the HTML sitemap if it\'s enabled.'=>'在 HTML 站点地图中包含作者档案（如果已启用）。','Include Authors Without Posts'=>'包含没有帖子的作者','Enable this option to include authors in the sitemap even if they have not created any posts. This ensures all author archives are listed, regardless of content availability.'=>'启用此选项可将作者包含在站点地图中，即使他们没有创建任何帖子。这可确保列出所有作者档案，无论内容可用性如何。','Exclude User Roles'=>'排除用户角色','Selected roles will be excluded from the XML &amp; HTML sitemaps.'=>'选定的角色将从 XML 和 XML 中排除。 HTML 站点地图。','Exclude Users'=>'排除用户','Add user IDs, separated by commas, to exclude them from the sitemap.'=>'添加用逗号分隔的用户 ID，以将其从站点地图中排除。','Rank Math generates the default Sitemaps only and WPML takes care of the rest. When a search engine bot visits any post/page, it is shown hreflang tag that helps it crawl the translated pages. This is one of the recommended methods by Google. Please %s'=>'Rank Math 仅生成默认站点地图，WPML 负责其余部分。当搜索引擎机器人访问任何帖子/页面时，会显示 hreflang 标签，帮助其抓取翻译后的页面。这是Google推荐的方法之一。请%s','read here'=>'阅读此处','Links Per Sitemap'=>'每个站点地图的链接数','Max number of links on each sitemap page.'=>'每个站点地图页面上的最大链接数。','Images in Sitemaps'=>'站点地图中的图像','Include reference to images from the post content in sitemaps. This helps search engines index the important images on your pages.'=>'在站点地图中包含对帖子内容中的图像的引用。这有助于搜索引擎为您页面上的重要图像建立索引。','Include Featured Images'=>'包含特色图像','Include the Featured Image too, even if it does not appear directly in the post content.'=>'也包含特色图像，即使它没有直接出现在帖子内容中。','Exclude Posts'=>'排除帖子','Enter post IDs of posts you want to exclude from the sitemap, separated by commas. This option **applies** to all posts types including posts, pages, and custom post types.'=>'输入要从站点地图中排除的帖子的帖子 ID，以逗号分隔。此选项**适用于**所有帖子类型，包括帖子、页面和自定义帖子类型。','Exclude Terms'=>'排除术语','Add term IDs, separated by comma. This option is applied for all taxonomies.'=>'添加术语 ID，以逗号分隔。此选项适用于所有分类。','Enable the HTML sitemap.'=>'启用 HTML 站点地图。','Display Format'=>'显示格式','Choose how you want to display the HTML sitemap.'=>'选择 HTML 站点地图的显示方式。','Shortcode'=>'短代码','Page'=>'页面','Use this shortcode to display the HTML sitemap.'=>'使用此短代码显示 HTML 站点地图。','Selected page: '=>'所选页面：','Selected page: <a href="%s" target="_blank" class="rank-math-selected-page">%s</a>'=>'所选页面：<a href="%s" target="_blank" class="rank-math-selected-page">%s</a>','Select the page to display the HTML sitemap. Once the settings are saved, the sitemap will be displayed below the content of the selected page.'=>'选择要显示 HTML 站点地图的页面。保存设置后，站点地图将显示在所选页面内容的下方。','Select a page'=>'选择页面','Sort By'=>'排序依据','Choose how you want to sort the items in the HTML sitemap.'=>'选择 HTML 站点地图中项目的排序方式。','Published Date'=>'发布日期','Modified Date'=>'修改日期','Alphabetical'=>'按字母顺序排列','Post ID'=>'帖子 ID','Show Dates'=>'显示日期','Show published dates for each post & page.'=>'显示每个帖子的发布日期& 页面。','Item Titles'=>'项目标题','Show the post/term titles, or the SEO titles in the HTML sitemap.'=>'在 HTML 站点地图中显示帖子/术语标题或 SEO 标题。','SEO Titles'=>'SEO 标题','To configure meta tags for your media attachment pages, you need to first %s to parent.'=>'要为媒体附件页面配置元标记，您需要先 %s 到父级。','disable redirect attachments'=>'禁用重定向附件','Include this post type in the XML sitemap.'=>'在 XML 站点地图中包含此帖子类型。','Include this post type in the HTML sitemap if it\'s enabled.'=>'在以下情况下在 HTML 站点地图中包含此帖子类型：已启用。','Image Custom Fields'=>'图像自定义字段','Insert custom field (post meta) names which contain image URLs to include them in the sitemaps. Add one per line.'=>'插入包含图像 URL 的自定义字段（后元）名称，以将其包含在站点地图中。每行添加一个。','Include archive pages for terms of this taxonomy in the XML sitemap.'=>'在 XML 站点地图中包含此分类术语的存档页面。','Include archive pages for terms of this taxonomy in the HTML sitemap.'=>'在 HTML 站点地图中包含此分类术语的存档页面。','Include Empty Terms'=>'包含空术语','Include archive pages of terms that have no posts associated.'=>'包含没有关联帖子的术语的存档页面。','KML File'=>'KML 文件','This KML File is generated by <a href="%s" target="_blank">Rank Math WordPress SEO Plugin</a>. It is used to provide location information to Google.'=>'此 KML 文件由 <a href="%s" target="_blank">Rank Math WordPress SEO 插件</a>生成。它用于向 Google 提供位置信息。','Learn more about <a href="%s" target="_blank">KML File</a>.'=>'详细了解 <a href="%s" target="_blank">KML 文件</a>。','<a href="%s">&#8592; Sitemap Index</a>'=>'<a href="%s">&#8592;站点地图索引</a>','Phone number'=>'电话号码','Latitude'=>'纬度','Longitude'=>'经度','XML Sitemap'=>'XML站点地图','This XML Sitemap is generated by <a href="%s" target="_blank">Rank Math WordPress SEO Plugin</a>. It is what search engines like Google use to crawl and re-crawl posts/pages/products/images/archives on your website.'=>'此XML站点地图由<a href="%s" target="_blank">Rank Math WordPress SEO插件</a>生成。 Google 等搜索引擎使用它来抓取和重新抓取您网站上的帖子/页面/产品/图片/档案。','Learn more about <a href="%s" target="_blank">XML Sitemaps</a>.'=>'详细了解 <a href="%s" target="_blank">XML 站点地图</a>。','This XML Sitemap Index file contains <strong>%s</strong> sitemaps.'=>'此 XML 站点地图索引文件包含 <strong>%s</strong> 站点地图。','Last Modified'=>'上次修改时间','This XML Sitemap contains <strong>%s</strong> URLs.'=>'此 XML 站点地图包含 <strong>%s</strong> URL。','Last Mod.'=>'上次修改。','Unable to create backup this time.'=>'这次无法创建备份。','Backup created successfully.'=>'备份创建成功。','Backup does not exist.'=>'备份不存在。','Backup restored successfully.'=>'备份恢复成功。','No backup key found to delete.'=>'找不到要删除的备份密钥。','Backup successfully deleted.'=>'备份成功删除。','The error log cannot be retrieved.'=>'无法检索错误日志。','The error log cannot be retrieved: Error log file is too large.'=>'无法检索错误日志检索到：错误日志文件太大。','Settings could not be imported:'=>'无法导入设置：','Settings could not be imported: Upload failed.'=>'无法导入设置：上传失败。','Uploaded file could not be read.'=>'无法读取上传的文件。','Settings successfully imported. Your old configuration has been saved as a backup.'=>'设置已成功导入。您的旧配置已保存为备份。','No settings found to be imported.'=>'未找到可导入的设置。','Sorry, you are not authorized to Import/Export the settings.'=>'抱歉，您无权导入/导出设置。','Invalid action selected.'=>'选择的操作无效。