ion'=>'作者描述','Author\'s biographical info of the current post, page or author archive.'=>'当前帖子、页面或作者存档的作者传记信息。','Example Post title'=>'帖子标题示例','Variable names can only contain alphanumeric characters, underscores and dashes.'=>'变量名称只能包含字母数字字符、下划线和破折号。','The variable has already been registered.'=>'变量已注册。','Separator Character'=>'分隔符','Separator character, as set in the Title Settings'=>'分隔符，如标题中设置设置','Search Query'=>'搜索查询','Search query (only available on search results page)'=>'搜索查询（仅在搜索结果页上可用）','example search'=>'示例搜索','Counter'=>'计数器','Starts at 1 and increments by 1.'=>'从 1 开始并以 1 递增。','File Name'=>'文件名','File Name of the attachment'=>'附件的文件名','Site Title'=>'网站标题','Title of the site'=>'网站标题','Site Description'=>'站点描述','Description of the site'=>'站点描述','Current Date'=>'当前日期','Current server date'=>'当前服务器日期','Current Day'=>'当前日期','Current server day'=>'当前服务器日期','Current Month'=>'当前月份','Current server month'=>'当前服务器月份','Current Year'=>'当前年份','Current server year'=>'当前服务器年份','Current Time'=>'当前时间','Current server time'=>'当前服务器时间','Current Time (advanced)'=>'当前时间（高级）','Current server time with custom formatting pattern.'=>'采用自定义格式模式的当前服务器时间。','Organization Name'=>'组织名称','The Organization Name added in Local SEO Settings.'=>'在本地 SEO 设置中添加的组织名称。','Organization Logo added in Local SEO Settings.'=>'在本地 SEO 设置中添加组织徽标。','Organization URL added in Local SEO Settings.'=>'在本地 SEO 设置中添加组织 URL。','%s Title'=>'%s 标题','%s Description'=>'%s 描述','Custom Term title.'=>'自定义术语标题。','Custom Term description.'=>'自定义术语描述。','Post Title'=>'帖子标题','Title of the current post/page'=>'当前帖子/页面的标题','Post Title of parent page'=>'父页面的帖子标题','Title of the parent page of the current post/page'=>'当前帖子/页面的父页面标题','Post Excerpt'=>'帖子摘录','Excerpt of the current post (or auto-generated if it does not exist)'=>'当前帖子的摘录（如果不存在则自动生成）','Excerpt of the current post (without auto-generation)'=>'当前帖子的摘录（不自动生成）','Post Excerpt Only'=>'仅帖子摘录','Custom or Generated SEO Title of the current post/page'=>'当前帖子/页面的自定义或生成的 SEO