iption'=>'术语描述','Current term description'=>'当前术语描述','Example Term Description'=>'示例术语描述','Custom Term (advanced)'=>'自定义术语（高级）','Custom term value.'=>'自定义术语值。','Custom term value'=>'自定义术语值','Custom Term description'=>'自定义术语描述','The $id variable is required.'=>'$id 变量是必需的。','Example'=>'示例','The $%1$s is required for variable %2$s.'=>'变量 %2$s 需要 $%1$s。','The redirection you are trying to create may cause an infinite loop. Please check the source and destination URLs. The redirection has been deactivated.'=>'您尝试创建的重定向可能会导致无限循环。请检查源 URL 和目标 URL。重定向已停用。','The redirection you are trying to update may cause an infinite loop. Please check the source and destination URLs.'=>'您尝试更新的重定向可能会导致无限循环。请检查源网址和目标网址。','Please add at least one valid source URL.'=>'请添加至少一个有效的源网址。','Invalid type.'=>'类型无效。','Module slug'=>'模块 slug','Invalid module'=>'模块无效','Module state either on or off'=>'模块状态打开或关闭','Post scores'=>'发布分数','Action to perform'=>'要执行的操作','Mode to set'=>'要设置的模式','Site disconnected successfully.'=>'站点已成功断开连接。','The current theme does not have "post-thumbnails" support.'=>'当前主题不支持“后缩略图”。','Sorry, you don\'t have the required permissions to access this page.'=>'抱歉，您没有访问此页面所需的权限。','The post could not be found.'=>'找不到该帖子。','Site token'=>'站点令牌','URL to get HTML tags for.'=>'用于获取 HTML 标签的 URL。','Selected posts to update the data for.'=>'要更新其数据的选定帖子。','Sorry, you are not allowed to create/update redirection.'=>'抱歉，您无权创建/更新重定向。','Sorry, you are not allowed to create/update schema.'=>'抱歉，您无权创建/更新结构化数据。','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit homepage SEO settings.'=>'抱歉，您无权编辑主页 SEO 设置。','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit this post type.'=>'抱歉，您无权编辑此帖子类型。','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit this post.'=>'抱歉，您无权编辑此帖子。','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit this term.'=>'抱歉，您无权编辑此术语。','Invalid term ID.'=>'术语 ID 无效。','Sorry, field is empty which is not allowed.'=>'抱歉，字段为空，这是不允许的。','Sorry, the field contains invalid characters.'=>'抱歉，该字段包含无效字符。','Current Step'=>'当前步骤','Current Step Data'=>'当前步骤数据','Enable Tracking'=>'启用跟踪','Object unique id'=>'对象唯一ID','Object Type i.e. post, term, user'=>'对象类型，即帖子、术语、用户','Whether the object has a redirect or not'=>'对象是否有重定向','Redirection ID'=>'重定向ID','Redirection URL'=>'重定向 URL','Meta to add or update data.'=>'用于添加或更新数据的元。','schemas to add or update data.'=>'用于添加或更新数据的结构化数据。','Enable breadcrumbs function'=>'启用面包屑功能','Turning off breadcrumbs will hide breadcrumbs inserted in template files too.'=>'关闭面包屑也会隐藏模板文件中插入的面包屑。','This option cannot be changed since your theme has added the support for Rank Math Breadcrumbs using: %s'=>'此选项无法更改，因为您的主题已使用以下方式添加了对排名数学面包屑的支持： %s','Separator character or string that appears between breadcrumb items.'=>'出现在面包屑项目之间的分隔符或字符串。','Show Homepage Link'=>'显示主页链接','Display homepage breadcrumb in trail.'=>'在跟踪中显示主页面包屑。','Homepage label'=>'主页标签','Label used for homepage link (first item) in breadcrumbs.'=>'用于面包屑中主页链接（第一项）的标签。','Homepage Link'=>'主页链接','Link to use for homepage (first item) in breadcrumbs.'=>'用于以下位置中主页（第一项）的链接面包屑。','Prefix Breadcrumb'=>'前缀面包屑','Prefix for the breadcrumb path.'=>'面包屑路径的前缀。','Archive Format'=>'存档格式','Format the label used for archive pages.'=>'设置用于存档页面的标签的格式。','Search Results Format'=>'搜索结果格式','Format the label used for search results pages.'=>'设置用于搜索结果页面的标签的格式。','404 label'=>'404 标签','Label used for 404 error item in breadcrumbs.'=>'用于面包屑中 404 错误项目的标签。','Hide Post Title'=>'隐藏帖子标题','Hide Post title from Breadcrumb.'=>'隐藏面包屑中的帖子标题。','Show Category(s)'=>'显示类别','If category is a child category, show all ancestor categories.'=>'如果类别是子类别，则显示所有祖先类别。','Hide Taxonomy Name'=>'隐藏分类名称','Hide Taxonomy Name from Breadcrumb.'=>'从面包屑中隐藏分类名称。','Show Blog Page'=>'显示博客页面','Show Blog Page in Breadcrumb.'=>'在面包屑中显示博客页面。','.htaccess file not found.'=>'未找到 .htaccess 文件。','.htaccess file is not writable.'=>'.htaccess 文件不可写。','I understand the risks and I want to edit the file'=>'我了解风险，我想编辑该文件','Be careful when editing the htaccess file, it is easy to make mistakes and break your site. If that happens, you can restore the file to its state <strong>before the last edit</strong> by replacing the htaccess file with the backup copy created by Rank Math in the same directory (<em>.htaccess_back_xxxxxx</em>) using an FTP client.'=>'编辑 htaccess 时请小心文件，很容易出错并破坏您的网站。如果发生这种情况，您可以使用 FTP 客户端将 htaccess 文件替换为 Rank Math 在同一目录 (<em>.htaccess_back_xxxxxx</em>) 中创建的备份副本，从而将文件恢复到<strong>上次编辑之前</strong>的状态。','Strip Category Base'=>'删除类别库','Remove /category/ from category archive URLs. %s <br>E.g. <code>example.com/category/my-category/</code> becomes <code>example.com/my-category</code>'=>'从类别存档 URL 中删除 /category/。 %s <br>例如<code>example.com/category/my-category/</code> 变为 <code>example.com/my-category</code>','Why do this?'=>'为什么要这样做？','Redirection Manager'=>'重定向管理器','Redirections Manager'=>'重定向管理器','Please enable Redirections module.'=>'请启用重定向模块。','Redirect Attachments'=>'重定向附件','Redirect all attachment page URLs to the post they appear in. For more advanced redirection control, use the built-in %s.'=>'将所有附件页面 URL 重定向到它们出现的帖子。要获得更高级的重定向控制，请使用内置%s。','Redirect Orphan Attachments'=>'重定向孤立附件','Redirect attachments without a parent post to this URL. Leave empty for no redirection.'=>'将没有父帖子的附件重定向到此 URL。留空表示不重定向。','Nofollow External Links'=>'Nofollow 外部链接','Automatically add <code>rel="nofollow"</code> attribute for external links appearing in your posts, pages, and other post types. The attribute is dynamically applied when the content is displayed, and the stored content is not changed.'=>'自动为您的帖子、页面和其他帖子类型中出现的外部链接添加 <code>rel="nofollow"</code> 属性。该属性在内容显示时动态应用，存储的内容不会改变。','Nofollow Image File Links'=>'Nofollow 图片文件链接','Automatically add <code>rel="nofollow"</code> attribute for links pointing to external image files. The attribute is dynamically applied when the content is displayed, and the stored content is not changed.'=>'自动为指向外部图片文件的链接添加 <code>rel="nofollow"</code> 属性。该属性在显示内容时动态应用，并且存储的内容不会更改。','Nofollow Domains'=>'Nofollow 域','Only add <code>nofollow</code> attribute for the link if target domain is in this list. Add one per line. Leave empty to apply nofollow for <strong>ALL</strong> external domains.'=>'仅当目标域在此列表中时，才为链接添加 <code>nofollow</code> 属性。每行添加一个。留空可对<strong>所有</strong>外部域应用nofollow。','Nofollow Exclude Domains'=>'Nofollow排除域','The <code>nofollow</code> attribute <strong>will not be added</strong> for the link if target domain is in this list. Add one per line.'=>'如果目标域在此列表中，则不会为链接添加<code>nofollow</code>属性<strong></strong>。每行添加一个。','Open External Links in New Tab/Window'=>'在新选项卡/窗口中打开外部链接','Automatically add <code>target="_blank"</code> attribute for external links appearing in your posts, pages, and other post types to make them open in a new browser tab or window. The attribute is dynamically applied when the content is displayed, and the stored content is not changed.'=>'自动为帖子、页面和其他帖子类型中出现的外部链接添加 <code>target="_blank"</code> 属性，以使它们在新的浏览器选项卡或窗口中打开。显示内容时会动态应用该属性，并且存储的内容不会更改。','Headless CMS Support'=>'Headless CMS 支持','Enable this option to register a REST API endpoint that returns the HTML meta tags for a given URL. %s'=>'启用此选项可注册返回给定 URL 的 HTML 元标记的 REST API 端点。 %s','Read more'=>'阅读更多','Show SEO Score to Visitors'=>'向访问者显示 SEO 分数','Proudly display the calculated SEO Score as a badge on the front end. It can be disabled for specific posts in the post editor.'=>'在前端自豪地显示计算出的 SEO 分数作为徽章。可以在帖子编辑器中针对特定帖子禁用此功能。','SEO Score Post Types'=>'SEO 得分帖子类型','SEO Score Template'=>'SEO 得分模板','Change the styling for the front end SEO score badge.'=>'更改前端 SEO 得分徽章的样式。','Circle'=>'圆形','Square'=>'方形','SEO Score Position'=>'SEO 得分位置','Display the badges automatically, or insert the %1$s shortcode in your posts and the %2$s template tag in your theme template files.'=>'自动显示徽章，或在帖子中插入 %1$s 短代码，在主题模板中插入 %2$s 模板标记文件。','Below Content'=>'以下内容','Above Content'=>'上方内容','Above & Below Content'=>'上方和下方内容','Custom (use shortcode)'=>'自定义（使用简码）','Support Us with a Link'=>'通过链接支持我们','If you are showing the SEO scores on the front end, this option will insert a %1$s backlink to RankMath.com to show your support. You can change the link & the text by using this %2$s.'=>'如果您在前端显示 SEO 分数，此选项将插入 %1$s 反向链接到 RankMath.com 以表示您的支持。您可以使用此 %2$s 更改链接和文本。','filter'=>'过滤器','Usage Tracking'=>'使用情况跟踪','Share anonymous usage data to help us improve Rank Math. No personal info is collected.'=>'共享匿名使用数据以帮助我们提高排名数学。不会收集任何个人信息。','Learn more about what data is and isn\'t tracked.'=>'详细了解哪些数据被跟踪和哪些数据未被跟踪。','RSS Before Content'=>'内容之前的 RSS','Add content before each post in your site feeds.'=>'在网站源中的每个帖子之前添加内容。','RSS After Content'=>'内容之后的 RSS','Add content after each post in your site feeds.'=>'在网站源中的每个帖子之后添加内容。','Available variables'=>'可用变量','Variable'=>'变量','A link to the archive for the post author, with the authors name as anchor text.'=>'指向帖子作者的存档的链接，其中包含作者姓名作为锚文本。','A link to the post, with the title as anchor text.'=>'指向帖子的链接，以标题作为锚文本。','A link to your site, with your site\'s name as anchor text.'=>'指向您网站的链接，以您网站的名称作为锚文本。','A link to your site, with your site\'s name and description as anchor text.'=>'指向您网站的链接，以您网站的名称和说明作为锚文本。','Featured image of the article.'=>'文章的精选图片。','Google Search Console'=>'Google Search Console','Enter your Google Search Console verification HTML code or ID. Learn how to get it: %s'=>'输入您的 Google Search Console 验证 HTML 代码或 ID。了解如何获取它：%s','Search Console Verification Page'=>'搜索控制台验证页','Bing Webmaster Tools'=>'Bing 网站站长工具','Enter your Bing Webmaster Tools verification HTML code or ID. Get it here: %s'=>'输入您的 Bing 网站站长工具验证 HTML 代码或 ID。在这里获取：%s','Bing Webmaster Verification Page'=>'Bing站长验证页面','Baidu Webmaster Tools'=>'百度站长工具','Enter your Baidu Webmaster Tools verification HTML code or ID. Learn how to get it: %s'=>'输入您的百度站长工具验证HTML代码或ID。了解如何获取它：%s','Yandex Verification ID'=>'Yandex 验证 ID','Enter your Yandex verification HTML code or ID. Learn how to get it: %s'=>'输入您的 Yandex 验证 HTML 代码或 ID。了解如何获取它：%s','Yandex.Webmaster Page'=>'Yandex.Webmaster 页面','Pinterest Verification ID'=>'Pinterest 验证 ID','Enter your Pinterest verification HTML code or ID. Learn how to get it: %s'=>'输入您的 Pinterest 验证 HTML 代码或 ID。了解如何获取它：%s','Pinterest Account'=>'Pinterest 帐户','Norton Safe Web Verification ID'=>'诺顿安全网络验证 ID','Enter your Norton Safe Web verification HTML code or ID. Learn how to get it: %s'=>'输入您的诺顿安全网络验证 HTML 代码或 ID。了解如何获取它：%s','Norton Ownership Verification Page'=>'诺顿所有权验证页面','Custom Webmaster Tags'=>'自定义网站站长标记','Enter your custom webmaster tags. Only %s tags are allowed.'=>'输入您的自定义网站站长标记。仅允许 %s 标签。','Author Archives'=>'作者档案','Enables or disables Author Archives. If disabled, the Author Archives are redirected to your homepage. To avoid duplicate content issues, noindex author archives if you keep them enabled.'=>'启用或禁用作者档案。如果禁用，作者档案将重定向到您的主页。为了避免重复内容问题，如果您保持启用状态，则 noindex 作者档案。','Disabled'=>'禁用','Enabled'=>'启用','Author Base'=>'作者基础','Change the <code>/author/</code> part in author archive URLs.'=>'更改作者档案 URL 中的 <code>/author/</code> 部分。','Author Robots Meta'=>'作者机器人元数据','Select custom robots meta for author page, such as <code>nofollow</code>, <code>noarchive</code>, etc. Otherwise the default meta will be used, as set in the Global Meta tab.'=>'为作者页面选择自定义机器人元，例如 <code>nofollow</code>、<code>noarchive</code>、等等。否则将使用默认元，如“全局 Meta”选项卡中设置的那样。','Custom values for robots meta tag on author page.'=>'作者页面上机器人元标记的自定义值。','Author Advanced Robots'=>'作者高级机器人','Author Archive Title'=>'作者存档标题','Title tag on author archives. SEO options for specific authors can be set with the meta box available in the user profiles.'=>'作者档案上的标题标签。可以使用用户配置文件中可用的元框设置特定作者的 SEO 选项。','Author Archive Description'=>'作者档案描述','Author archive meta description. SEO options for specific author archives can be set with the meta box in the user profiles.'=>'作者档案元描述。可以使用用户个人资料中的元框设置特定作者档案的 SEO 选项。','Slack Enhanced Sharing'=>'Slack 增强共享','When the option is enabled and an author archive is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (name & total number of posts).'=>'启用该选项并在 Slack 上共享作者档案时，将显示附加信息（姓名和帖子总数）。','Add SEO Controls'=>'添加 SEO 控件','Add SEO Controls for user profile pages. Access to the Meta Box can be fine tuned with code, using a special filter hook.'=>'为用户个人资料页面添加 SEO 控件。可以使用特殊的过滤器挂钩通过代码微调对元框的访问。','Robots Meta'=>'机器人元','Default values for robots meta tag. These can be changed for individual posts, taxonomies, etc.'=>'机器人元标记的默认值。这些可以针对单个帖子、分类法等进行更改。','Advanced Robots Meta'=>'Advanced Robots Meta','Noindex Empty Category and Tag Archives'=>'Noindex 空类别和标签档案','Setting empty archives to <code>noindex</code> is useful for avoiding indexation of thin content pages and dilution of page rank. As soon as a post is added, the page is updated to <code>index</code>.'=>'将空档案设置为 <code>noindex</code> 对于避免内容薄页的索引和页面排名的稀释非常有用。添加帖子后，页面将更新为 <code>index</code>。','You can use the separator character in titles by inserting <code>%separator%</code> or <code>%sep%</code> in the title fields.'=>'您可以通过在标题字段中插入 <code>%separator%</code> 或 <code>%sep%</code> 来在标题中使用分隔符。','Rewrite Titles'=>'重写标题','Your current theme doesn\'t support title-tag. Enable this option to rewrite page, post, category, search and archive page titles.'=>'您当前的主题不支持标题标签。启用此选项可重写页面、帖子、类别、搜索和存档页面标题。','Capitalize Titles'=>'大写标题','Automatically capitalize the first character of each word in the titles.'=>'自动大写标题中每个单词的第一个字符。','OpenGraph Thumbnail'=>'OpenGraph 缩略图','When a featured image or an OpenGraph Image is not set for individual posts/pages/CPTs, this image will be used as a fallback thumbnail when your post is shared on Facebook. The recommended image size is 1200 x 630 pixels.'=>'如果未为单个帖子/页面/CPT 设置特色图像或 OpenGraph 图像，则当您的帖子在 Facebook 上共享时，此图像将用作后备缩略图。建议的图像尺寸为 1200 x 630 像素。','Twitter Card Type'=>'Twitter 卡片类型','Card type selected when creating a new post. This will also be applied for posts without a card type selected.'=>'创建新帖子时选择的卡片类型。这也适用于未选择卡片类型的帖子。','Summary Card with Large Image'=>'大图像摘要卡','Summary Card'=>'摘要卡','Static page is set as the front page (WP Dashboard > Settings > Reading). To add SEO title, description, and meta for the homepage, please click here: %s'=>'静态页面设置为首页（WP 仪表板 > 设置 > 阅读）。要为主页添加 SEO 标题、描述和元数据，请单击此处：%s','Homepage Title'=>'主页标题','Homepage title tag.'=>'主页标题标签。','Homepage Meta Description'=>'主页元描述','Homepage meta description.'=>'主页元描述。','Homepage Robots Meta'=>'主页机器人元','Select custom robots meta for homepage, such as <code>nofollow</code>, <code>noarchive</code>, etc. Otherwise the default meta will be used, as set in the Global Meta tab.'=>'为主页选择自定义机器人元，例如 <code>nofollow</code>、<code>noarchive</code> 等。否则将使用默认元，如“全局 Meta”选项卡中设置的那样。','Custom values for robots meta tag on homepage.'=>'主页上机器人元标记的自定义值。','Homepage Advanced Robots'=>'主页高级机器人','Homepage Title for Facebook'=>'Facebook 的主页标题','Title of your site when shared on Facebook, Twitter and other social networks.'=>'在 Facebook、Twitter 和其他社交网络上共享时您的网站的标题。','Homepage Description for Facebook'=>'Facebook 的主页描述','Description of your site when shared on Facebook, Twitter and other social networks.'=>'在 Facebook、Twitter 和其他社交网络上共享时您的网站的描述。','Homepage Thumbnail for Facebook'=>'Facebook 的主页缩略图','Image displayed when your homepage is shared on Facebook and other social networks. Use images that are at least 1200 x 630 pixels for the best display on high resolution devices.'=>'您的主页在 Facebook 和其他社交网络上共享时显示的图像。使用至少 1200 x 630 像素的图像，以便在高分辨率设备上获得最佳显示效果。','URL of the item.'=>'项目的 URL。','Date Archives'=>'日期存档','Enable or disable the date archives (e.g: %s). If this option is disabled, the date archives will be redirected to the homepage.'=>'启用或禁用日期存档（例如：%s）。如果禁用此选项，日期存档将被重定向到主页。','Date Archive Title'=>'日期存档标题','Title tag on day/month/year based archives.'=>'基于日/月/年的存档上的标题标签。','Date Archive Description'=>'日期存档描述','Date archive description.'=>'日期存档描述。','Date Robots Meta'=>'日期机器人元','Custom values for robots meta tag on date page.'=>'日期页面上机器人元标记的自定义值。','Date Advanced Robots'=>'日期高级机器人','404 Title'=>'404标题','Title tag on 404 Not Found error page.'=>'404 Not Found 错误页面上的标题标签。','Search Results Title'=>'搜索结果标题','Title tag on search results page.'=>'搜索结果页面上的标题标签。','Noindex Search Results'=>'Noindex 搜索结果','Prevent search results pages from getting indexed by search engines. Search results could be considered to be thin content and prone to duplicate content issues.'=>'防止搜索结果页面被搜索引擎索引。搜索结果可能被视为内容贫乏，容易出现重复内容问题。','Noindex Subpages'=>'Noindex 子页面','Prevent all paginated pages from getting indexed by search engines.'=>'防止所有分页页面被搜索引擎索引。','Noindex Paginated Single Pages'=>'Noindex 分页单页','Prevent paginated pages of single pages and posts to show up in the search results. This also applies for the Blog page.'=>'防止单页和帖子的分页页面显示在搜索结果中。这也适用于博客页面。','Noindex Password Protected Pages'=>'Noindex 密码保护页面','Prevent password protected pages & posts from getting indexed by search engines.'=>'防止受密码保护的页面和帖子被搜索引擎索引。','When the option is enabled and a %s is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (estimated time to read and author).'=>'启用该选项并在 Slack 上共享 %s 时，将显示附加信息（预计阅读和创作时间）。','When the option is enabled and a page is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (estimated time to read).'=>'启用该选项并在 Slack 上共享页面时，将显示附加信息（预计阅读和创作时间）。阅读）。','When the option is enabled and a product is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (price & availability).'=>'启用该选项并在 Slack 上共享产品时，将显示附加信息（价格和可用性）。','When the option is enabled and a product is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (price).'=>'启用该选项并在 Slack 上共享产品时，将显示附加信息（价格）。','Single %s Title'=>'单个 %s 标题','Default title tag for single %s pages. This can be changed on a per-post basis on the post editor screen.'=>'单个 %s 页面的默认标题标记。这可以在帖子编辑器屏幕上针对每个帖子进行更改。','Single %s Description'=>'单个 %s 描述','Default description for single %s pages. This can be changed on a per-post basis on the post editor screen.'=>'单个 %s 页面的默认描述。可以在帖子编辑器屏幕上针对每个帖子进行更改。','%s Archive Title'=>'%s 存档标题','Title for %s archive pages.'=>'%s 存档页面的标题。','%s Archive Description'=>'%s 存档描述','Description for %s archive pages.'=>'%s 存档页面的描述。','Schema Type'=>'结构化数据类型','Default rich snippet selected when creating a new product.'=>'创建新产品时选择的默认丰富网页摘要。','Default rich snippet selected when creating a new post of this type. If %s is selected, it will be applied for all existing posts with no Schema selected.'=>'创建此类型的新帖子时选择的默认丰富网页摘要。如果选择 %s，它将应用于所有未选择结构化数据的现有帖子。','Schema type name in a field descriptionArticle'=>'文章','Headline'=>'标题','Google does not allow Person as the Publisher for articles. Organization will be used instead. You can read more about this <a href="%s" target="_blank">here</a>.'=>'Google 不允许个人作为文章的发布者。将使用组织来代替。您可以在<a href="%s" target="_blank">此处</a>阅读有关此内容的更多信息。','Article Type'=>'文章类型','Blog Post'=>'博客文章','News Article'=>'新闻文章','%s Robots Meta'=>'%s 机器人元数据','Select custom robots meta, such as <code>nofollow</code>, <code>noarchive</code>, etc. for single %s pages. Otherwise the default meta will be used, as set in the Global Meta tab.'=>'为单个 %s 页面选择自定义机器人元数据，例如 <code>nofollow</code>、<code>noarchive</code> 等。否则，将使用“全局 Meta”选项卡中设置的默认元。','Custom values for robots meta tag on %s.'=>'%s 上的机器人元标记的自定义值。','%s Advanced Robots Meta'=>'%s 高级机器人元','Enable Link Suggestions meta box for this post type, along with the Pillar Content feature.'=>'为此帖子类型启用链接建议元框以及支柱内容功能。','Link Suggestion Titles'=>'链接建议标题','Use the Focus Keyword as the default text for the links instead of the post titles.'=>'使用焦点关键字作为链接而不是帖子的默认文本标题。','Titles'=>'标题','Primary Taxonomy'=>'主要分类法','Choose which taxonomy you want to use with the Primary Term feature. This will also be the taxonomy shown in the Breadcrumbs when a single %1$s is being viewed.'=>'选择要与主要术语功能一起使用的分类法。当查看单个 %1$s 时，这也将是面包屑中显示的分类。','Thumbnail for Facebook'=>'Facebook 的缩略图','Image displayed when your page is shared on Facebook and other social networks. Use images that are at least 1200 x 630 pixels for the best display on high resolution devices.'=>'当您的页面在 Facebook 和其他社交网络上共享时显示的图像。使用至少 1200 x 630 像素的图像，以便在高分辨率设备上获得最佳显示效果。','Bulk Editing'=>'批量编辑','Add bulk editing columns to the post listing screen.'=>'将批量编辑列添加到帖子列表屏幕。','Read Only'=>'只读','Add SEO controls for the editor screen to customize SEO options for posts in this post type.'=>'为编辑器屏幕添加 SEO 控件，以便为该帖子类型的帖子自定义 SEO 选项。','Custom Fields'=>'自定义字段','List of custom fields name to include in the Page analysis. Add one per line.'=>'要包含在页面分析中的自定义字段名称列表。每行添加一个。','Facebook Page URL'=>'Facebook 页面 URL','Enter your complete Facebook page URL here. eg:'=>'在此输入您的完整 Facebook 页面 URL。例如：','Facebook Authorship'=>'Facebook 作者身份','Insert personal Facebook profile URL to show Facebook Authorship when your articles are being shared on Facebook. eg:'=>'插入个人 Facebook 个人资料 URL，以便在 Facebook 上共享您的文章时显示 Facebook 作者身份。例如：','Facebook Admin'=>'Facebook 管理员','Enter %s. Use a comma to separate multiple IDs. Alternatively, you can enter an app ID below.'=>'输入 %s。使用逗号分隔多个 ID。或者，您可以在下面输入应用程序 ID。','Facebook App'=>'Facebook 应用程序','Enter %s. Alternatively, you can enter a user ID above.'=>'输入 %s。或者，您可以在上面输入用户 ID。','Facebook Secret'=>'Facebook 秘密','Enter alphanumeric secret ID. %s.'=>'输入字母数字秘密 ID。 %s.','Twitter Username'=>'Twitter 用户名','Enter the Twitter username of the author to add <code>twitter:creator</code> tag to posts. eg: <code>RankMathSEO</code>'=>'输入作者的 Twitter 用户名以将 <code>twitter:creator</code> 标签添加到帖子中。例如：<code>RankMathSEO</code>','Additional Profiles'=>'其他配置文件','%s Archive Titles'=>'%s 存档标题','Title tag for %s archives'=>'%s 存档的标题标签','%s Archive Descriptions'=>'%s 存档描述','Description for %s archives'=>'%s 存档的描述','%s Archives Robots Meta'=>'%s 存档机器人元数据','Select custom robots meta, such as <code>nofollow</code>, <code>noarchive</code>, etc. for %s archive pages. Otherwise the default meta will be used, as set in the Global Meta tab.'=>'选择自定义机器人元数据，例如 <code>nofollow</code>， <code>noarchive</code> 等，用于 %s 存档页面。否则，将使用“全局 Meta”选项卡中设置的默认元。','Custom values for robots meta tag on %s archives.'=>'%s 存档上的机器人元标记的自定义值。','%s Archives Advanced Robots Meta'=>'%s 存档高级机器人元','When the option is enabled and a term from this taxonomy is shared on Slack, additional information will be shown (the total number of items with this term).'=>'启用该选项并且在 Slack 上共享此分类中的术语时，将显示附加信息（包含此术语的项目总数）。','Add the SEO Controls for the term editor screen to customize SEO options for individual terms in this taxonomy.'=>'为术语编辑器屏幕添加 SEO 控件，以自定义此分类中各个术语的 SEO 选项分类。','Remove Snippet Data'=>'删除代码段数据','Remove schema data from %s.'=>'从 %s 中删除结构化数据数据。','Error: Nonce verification failed'=>'错误：Nonce 验证失败','Universal Analytics (UA) is no longer supported. Please connect your Google Analytics GA4 account by navigating to %1$sGeneral Settings → Analytics%2$s. For more details, refer to this guide: %3$sHow to Use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) Property with Rank Math%4$s.'=>'不再支持通用分析 (UA)。请导航至%1$s常规设置 → Analytics%2$s，连接您的 Google Analytics GA4 帐户。有关详细信息，请参阅本指南：%3$s如何将 Google Analytics 4 (GA4) 属性与 Rank Math%4$s 一起使用。','You are using the outdated WordPress, please update it to version %s or higher.'=>'您使用的是过时的 WordPress，请将其更新到版本 %s 或更高版本。','Rank Math requires PHP version %s or above. Please update PHP to run this plugin.'=>'Rank Math 需要 PHP 版本 %s 或更高版本。请更新 PHP 以运行此插件。','%1$s A filter to remove the Rank Math data from the database is present. Deactivating & Deleting this plugin will remove everything related to the Rank Math plugin. %2$s'=>'%1$s 存在用于从数据库中删除排名数学数据的过滤器。停用和删除此插件将删除与排名数学插件相关的所有内容。 %2$s','CAUTION:'=>'注意：','This action is IRREVERSIBLE.'=>'此操作不可逆转。','Getting Started'=>'入门','Documentation'=>'文档','block titleFAQ by Rank Math'=>'Rank Math 常见问题解答','block descriptionEasily add Schema-ready, SEO-friendly, Frequently Asked Questions to your content.'=>'轻松将符合结构化数据标准、对 SEO 友好的常见问题解答添加到您的内容中。','block keywordFAQ'=>'常见问题问题','block keywordFrequently Asked Questions'=>'架构','block keywordSchema'=>'SEO','block keywordSEO'=>'结构化数据','block keywordStructured Data'=>'Yoast','block keywordYoast'=>'排名数学','block keywordRank Math'=>'区块','block keywordBlock'=>'Block','block keywordMarkup'=>'标记','block keywordRich Snippet'=>'丰富的片段','block titleHowTo by Rank Math'=>'HowTo（按Rank Math）','block descriptionEasily add Schema-ready, SEO-friendly, HowTo block to your content.'=>'轻松将架构就绪、SEO 友好的HowTo 块添加到您的内容中。','block keywordHowTo'=>'HowTo','block titleSchema by Rank Math'=>'Schema（按Rank Math）','block descriptionAdd the Schema generated by Rank Math anywhere on your page using this Block.'=>'使用此块在页面上的任何位置添加由Rank Math 生成的架构。','block titleTable of Contents by Rank Math'=>'按Rank 的目录数学','block descriptionAutomatically generate the Table of Contents from the Headings added to this page.'=>'根据添加到此页面的标题自动生成目录。','Add a few images and/or videos to make your content appealing.'=>'添加一些图片和/或视频以使您的内容更具吸引力。','Content with images and/or video feels more inviting to users. It also helps supplement your textual content.'=>'包含图片和/或视频的内容对用户来说更具吸引力。它还有助于补充您的文本内容。','Your content contains images and/or video(s).'=>'您的内容包含图像和/或视频。','You are not using rich media like images or videos.'=>'您没有使用图像或视频等富媒体。','Add short and concise paragraphs for better readability and UX.'=>'添加简短而简洁的段落以提高可读性和用户体验。','Short paragraphs are easier to read and more pleasing to the eye. Long paragraphs scare the visitor, and they might result to SERPs looking for better readable content.'=>'短段落更易于阅读，也更赏心悦目。长段落会让访问者感到害怕，并且可能会导致 SERP 寻找更易读的内容。','You are using short paragraphs.'=>'您正在使用短段落。','At least one paragraph is long. Consider using short paragraphs.'=>'至少一个段落较长。请考虑使用短段落。','Use Table of Content to break-down your text.'=>'使用目录来分解您的文本。','Table of Contents help break down content into smaller, digestible chunks. It makes reading easier which in turn results in better rankings.'=>'目录有助于将内容分解成更小、更易理解的部分。它使阅读更容易，从而提高排名。','You seem to be using a %1$s to break-down your text.'=>'您似乎正在使用 %1$s 来分解您的文本。','You don\'t seem to be using a %1$s.'=>'您似乎没有使用 %1$s。','Keyword Density is 0. Aim for around 1% Keyword Density.'=>'关键词密度为 0。目标是关键词密度约为 1%。','There is no ideal keyword density percentage, but it should not be too high. The most important thing is to keep the copy natural.'=>'没有理想的关键词密度百分比，但不应太高。最重要的是保持文案的自然性。','Keyword Density is %1$s which is low, the Focus Keyword and combination appears %2$s times.'=>'关键词密度为%1$s，较低，焦点关键词及其组合出现了%2$s次。','Keyword Density is %1$s which is high, the Focus Keyword and combination appears %2$s times.'=>'关键词密度为%1$s，较高，焦点关键词及其组合出现了%2$s次。','Keyword Density is %1$s, the Focus Keyword and combination appears %2$s times.'=>'关键词密度为%1$s，焦点关键词及其组合出现%2$s次。','Use Focus Keyword at the beginning of your content.'=>'在内容开头使用焦点关键词。','The first 10% of the content should contain the Focus Keyword preferably at the beginning.'=>'内容的前 10％ 最好在开头包含焦点关键词。','Focus Keyword appears in the first 10% of the content.'=>'焦点关键词出现在内容的前10％。','Focus Keyword doesn\'t appear at the beginning of your content.'=>'焦点关键词没有出现在内容的开头。','Use Focus Keyword in the content.'=>'在内容中使用焦点关键词。','It is recommended to make the focus keyword appear in the post content too.'=>'建议让焦点关键词也出现在帖子内容中。','Focus Keyword found in the content.'=>'在内容中找到焦点关键词。','Focus Keyword doesn\'t appear in the content.'=>'焦点关键词未出现在内容中。','Add an image with your Focus Keyword as alt text.'=>'将带有焦点关键字的图像添加为 alt 文本。','It is recommended to add the focus keyword in the alt attribute of one or more images.'=>'建议在一个或多个图像的 alt 属性中添加焦点关键字。','We detected a gallery in your content & assuming that you added Focus Keyword in alt in at least one of the gallery images.'=>'我们在您的内容中检测到一个图库，并假设您在至少一个图库图像的 alt 中添加了焦点关键字。','Focus Keyword found in image alt attribute(s).'=>'在图像 alt 属性中找到了焦点关键字。','Focus Keyword not found in image alt attribute(s).'=>'在图像 alt 属性中未找到焦点关键字。','Add Focus Keyword to your SEO Meta Description.'=>'将焦点关键词添加到您的 SEO 元描述。','Make sure the focus keyword appears in the SEO description too.'=>'确保焦点关键词也出现在 SEO 描述中。','Focus Keyword used inside SEO Meta Description.'=>'SEO 元描述中使用的焦点关键词。','Focus Keyword not found in your SEO Meta Description.'=>'您的 SEO 元描述中未找到焦点关键字。','Use Focus Keyword in the URL.'=>'在 URL 中使用焦点关键词。','Include the focus keyword in the slug (permalink) of this post.'=>'在此帖子的 slug（永久链接）中包含焦点关键字。','Focus