rn flat 30% on every sale!'=>'每笔销售赚取 30% 佣金！','SEO Care'=>'SEO 关怀','Get expert help to grow your site\'s SEO'=>'获取专家帮助以提升您网站的 SEO','The plugin is currently not connected with your Rank Math account. Click on the button below to login or register for FREE using your '=>'该插件目前未与您的 Rank Math 帐户连接。点击下面的按钮使用您的登录或免费注册 ','Google account, Facebook account'=>'Google 帐户、Facebook 帐户',' or '=>' 或 ','your email account.'=>'您的电子邮件帐户。','You have successfully activated Rank Math. If you find the plugin useful, '=>'您已成功激活 Rank Math。如果您觉得该插件有用，','feel free to recommend it to your friends or colleagues.'=>'请随时推荐给您的朋友或同事。','You can\'t access this page.'=>'您无法访问此页面。','Failed! Try again'=>'失败！请重试','Saved'=>'已保存','Auto Update'=>'自动更新','You cannot turn on auto-updates to automatically update to stable versions of Rank Math as soon as they are released, because site wide plugins auto-update option is disabled on your site.'=>'您无法开启自动更新以在 Rank Math 稳定版发布后立即自动更新，因为您网站上的站点范围插件自动更新选项已禁用。','Turn on auto-updates to automatically update to stable versions of Rank Math as soon as they are released. The beta versions of Rank Math as soon as they are released. The beta versions will never install automatically.'=>'开启自动更新以在 Rank Math 稳定版发布后立即自动更新。Rank Math 测试版发布后也将立即更新。测试版永远不会自动安装。','Auto Update Plugin'=>'自动更新插件','When auto-updates are turned off, you can enable update notifications, to send an email to the site administrator when an update is available for Rank Math.'=>'当自动更新关闭时，您可以启用更新通知，以便在有 Rank Math 更新时向站点管理员发送电子邮件。','Update Notification Email'=>'更新通知邮件','Rank Math will not auto-update because you have rolled back to a previous version. Update to the latest version manually to make this option work again.'=>'Rank Math 不会自动更新，因为您已回滚到之前的版本。请手动更新到最新版本以使此选项再次生效。','Beta Opt-in'=>'测试版加入','You cannot turn on the Beta Tester feature because site wide plugins auto-update option is disabled on your site.'=>'您无法开启 Beta 测试功能，因为您网站上的站点范围插件自动更新选项已禁用。','You can take part in shaping Rank Math by test-driving the newest features and letting us know what you think. Turn on the Beta Tester feature to get notified about new beta releases. The beta version will not install automatically and you always have the option to ignore it.'=>'您可以通过试用最新功能并告诉我们您的想法来参与塑造 Rank Math。开启 Beta 测试功能以获取新测试版发布的通知。测试版不会自动安装，您始终可以选择忽略它。','It is not recommended to use the beta version on live production sites.'=>'不建议在生产环境中使用测试版。','Beta Tester'=>'Beta 测试','Rollback to Previous Version'=>'回滚到之前的版本','If you are facing issues after an update, you can reinstall a previous version with this tool.'=>'如果您在更新后遇到问题，可以使用此工具重新安装之前的版本。','Previous versions may not be secure or stable. Proceed with caution and always create a backup.'=>'之前的版本可能不安全或不稳定。请谨慎操作并始终创建备份。','Your Version'=>'您的版本','Rolled Back Version: '=>'已回滚版本：','Auto updates will not work, please update the plugin manually.'=>'自动更新将无法工作，请手动更新插件。','You are using the latest version of the plugin.'=>'您正在使用插件的最新版本。','This is the version you are using on this site.'=>'这是您在此站点上使用的版本。','Latest Stable Version'=>'最新稳定版','This is the latest version of the plugin.'=>'这是插件的最新版本。','Rollback Version'=>'回滚版本','Roll back to this version.'=>'回滚到此版本。','Install Version '=>'安装版本 ','Reinstalling, please wait…'=>'正在重新安装，请稍候…','Are you sure? You want to reset settings.'=>'确定吗？您想要重置设置。','Bulk Edit This Field'=>'批量编辑此字段','Save All Edits'=>'保存所有编辑','This is what will appear in the first line when this post shows up in the search results.'=>'这是此文章在搜索结果中显示时将出现在第一行的内容。','Permalink'=>'固定链接','Editing Homepage permalink is not possible.'=>'无法编辑首页固定链接。','This is the unique URL of this page, displayed below the post title in the search results.'=>'这是此页面的唯一 URL，在搜索结果中显示在文章标题下方。','This is what will appear as the description when this post shows up in the search results.'=>'这是此文章在搜索结果中显示时将作为描述的内容。','Rating: '=>'评分：','Preview'=>'预览','Desktop Preview'=>'桌面预览','Mobile Preview'=>'移动预览','Videos'=>'视频','News'=>'新闻','Maps'=>'地图','More'=>'更多','About 43,700,000 results (0.32 seconds) '=>'约 43,700,000 条结果（0.32 秒）','Noindex robots meta is enabled'=>'已启用 Noindex 机器人元标记','This page will not appear in search results. You can disable noindex in the Advanced tab.'=>'此页面不会出现在搜索结果中。您可以在高级选项卡中禁用 noindex。','Replace Image'=>'替换图片','Add Image'=>'添加图片','Remove Image'=>'移除图片','Upload at least 600x315px image. Recommended size is 1200x630px.'=>'上传至少 600x315px 的图片。推荐尺寸为 1200x630px。','Image is smaller than the minimum size, please select a different image.'=>'图片小于最小尺寸，请选择其他图片。','2 hrs'=>'2 小时','Customize the title, description and images of your post used while sharing on Facebook and Twitter.'=>'自定义在 Facebook 和 Twitter 上分享时使用的文章标题、描述和图片。','Add icon overlay to thumbnail'=>'为缩略图添加图标叠加','Icon overlay'=>'图标叠加','You can add custom thumbnail overlays with {{link}}Rank Math Pro{{/link}}.'=>'您可以使用 {{link}}Rank Math Pro{{/link}} 添加自定义缩略图叠加。','App Description'=>'应用描述','You can use this as a more concise description than what you may have on the app store. This field has a maximum of 200 characters. (optional)'=>'您可以使用比应用商店中更简洁的描述。此字段最多 200 个字符。（可选）','iPhone App Name'=>'iPhone 应用名称','The name of your app to show.'=>'要显示的应用名称。','iPhone App ID'=>'iPhone 应用 ID','The numeric representation of your app ID in the App Store.'=>'您的应用在 App Store 中的数字 ID。','iPhone App URL'=>'iPhone 应用 URL','Your app\'s custom URL scheme (must include ://).'=>'您的应用的自定义 URL 方案（必须包含 ://）。','iPad App Name'=>'iPad 应用名称','iPad App ID'=>'iPad 应用 ID','iPad App URL'=>'iPad 应用 URL','Google Play App Name'=>'Google Play 应用名称','Google Play App ID'=>'Google Play 应用 ID','Your app ID in the Google Play (.i.e. com.android.app)'=>'您在 Google Play 中的应用 ID（例如 com.android.app）','Google Play App URL'=>'Google Play 应用 URL','App Country'=>'应用国家/地区','If your application is not available in the US App Store, you must set this value to the two-letter country code for the App Store that contains your application.'=>'如果您的应用程序在美国 App Store 中不可用，您必须将此值设置为包含您应用程序的 App Store 的两个字母国家/地区代码。','Player URL'=>'播放器 URL','HTTPS URL to iFrame player. This must be a HTTPS URL which does not generate active mixed content warnings in a web browser. The audio or video player must not require plugins such as Adobe Flash.'=>'iFrame 播放器的 HTTPS URL。这必须是 HTTPS URL，不会在 Web 浏览器中生成活动混合内容警告。音频或视频播放器不得需要 Adobe Flash 等插件。','Player Size'=>'播放器尺寸','iFrame width and height, specified in pixels in the following format: 600x400.'=>'iFrame 宽度和高度，以像素为单位，格式如下：600x400。','Stream URL'=>'流 URL','Optional URL to raw stream that will be rendered in Twitter’s mobile applications directly. If provided, the stream must be delivered in the MPEG-4 container format (the .mp4 extension). The container can store a mix of audio and video with the following codecs: Video: H.264, Baseline Profile (BP), Level 3.0, up to 640 x 480 at 30 fps. Audio: AAC, Low Complexity Profile (LC).'=>'可选原始流 URL，将直接在 Twitter 移动应用中渲染。如果提供，流必须以 MPEG-4 容器格式（.mp4 扩展名）传输。容器可以存储以下编解码器的音频和视频混合：视频：H.264，Baseline Profile (BP)，Level 3.0，最高 640 x 480，30 fps。音频：AAC，Low Complexity Profile (LC)。','Stream Content Type'=>'流内容类型','The MIME type/subtype combination that describes the content contained in twitter:player:stream. Takes the form specified in RFC 6381. Currently supported content_type values are those defined in RFC 4337 (MIME Type Registration for MP4).'=>'描述 twitter:player:stream 中包含内容的 MIME 类型/子类型组合。采用 RFC 6381 中指定的格式。当前支持的 content_type 值是 RFC 4337（MP4 的 MIME 类型注册）中定义的值。','2h'=>'2小时','The card for your website will look little something like this!'=>'您网站的卡片将看起来像这样！','Use Data from Facebook Tab'=>'使用来自 Facebook 标签的数据','Card Type'=>'卡片类型','App Card'=>'应用卡片','Player Card'=>'播放器卡片','Video clips and audio streams have a special place on the Twitter platform thanks to the Player Card. Player Cards must be submitted for approval before they can be used. More information: '=>'视频剪辑和音频流在 Twitter 平台上有着特殊的地位，这要归功于播放器卡片。播放器卡片必须先提交审批才能使用。更多信息：','The App Card is a great way to represent mobile applications on Twitter and to drive installs. More information: '=>'应用卡片是在 Twitter 上展示移动应用程序和推动安装的好方法。更多信息：','Facebook'=>'Facebook','Twitter'=>'Twitter','Rate Rank Math SEO'=>'评价 Rank Math SEO','Hey, we noticed you are using Rank Math SEO plugin for more than a week now –{{em}}that\'s awesome!{{/em}} Could you please do us a BIG favor and give it a 5-star rating on WordPress to help us spread the word and boost our motivation?'=>'嘿，我们注意到您使用 Rank Math SEO 插件已超过一周——{{em}}太棒了！{{/em}} 您能帮我们一个大忙，在 WordPress 上给它一个 5 星评价，帮助我们传播并激励我们吗？','I already did. Please don\'t show this message again.'=>'我已经评价过了。请不要再显示此消息。','Social'=>'社交','Edit Snippet'=>'编辑摘要','Preview Snippet Editor'=>'预览摘要编辑器','Close'=>'关闭','Social Media Preview'=>'社交媒体预览','Here you can view and edit the thumbnail, title and description that will be displayed when your site is shared on social media.'=>'您可以在此处查看和编辑在社交媒体上分享您的网站时将显示的缩略图、标题和描述。','Click on the button below to view and edit the preview.'=>'点击下面的按钮查看和编辑预览。','Preview & Edit Social Media'=>'预览和编辑社交媒体','All Good'=>'一切正常','Errors'=>'错误','Additional'=>'附加','Title Readability'=>'标题可读性','Content Readability'=>'内容可读性','Read here to {{link}}Score 100/100{{/link}} '=>'阅读此处以{{link}}获得 100/100 分{{/link}} ','Activate your account by {{link}}connecting to Rank Math!{{/link}} '=>'通过{{link}}连接到 Rank Math!{{/link}}激活您的帐户 ','Want more? {{link}}{{strong}}Upgrade today to the PRO{{/strong}}{{/link}} version.'=>'想要更多？{{link}}{{strong}}立即升级到 PRO{{/strong}}{{/link}}版本。','Upgrade to re-order Focus Keywords'=>'升级以重新排序焦点关键词','Improve the SEO workflow'=>'改进 SEO 工作流程','Set different Primary Focus Keyword'=>'设置不同的主要焦点关键词','and many other premium SEO features'=>'以及许多其他高级 SEO 功能','Example: Rank Math SEO'=>'示例：Rank Math SEO','Show Intent'=>'显示意图','Trends'=>'趋势','Google Trends'=>'Google 趋势','Track Keyword Trends'=>'追踪关键词趋势','Data fetched directly from Google'=>'直接从 Google 获取的数据','Analyze search trends and compare keywords'=>'分析搜索趋势并比较关键词','See data from a particular Country or timeframe'=>'查看特定国家或时间段的数据','Insert keywords you want to rank for. Try to {{link}}attain 100/100 points{{/link}} for better chances of ranking.'=>'输入您想要排名的关键词。尝试{{link}}获得 100/100 分{{/link}}以获得更好的排名机会。','This post is Pillar Content'=>'此文章是支柱内容','Instructs search engines to index and show these pages in the search results'=>'指示搜索引擎索引并在搜索结果中显示这些页面','Nofollow'=>'Nofollow','This option prevents images on a page from being indexed by Google and other search engines'=>'此选项可防止页面上的图像被 Google 和其他搜索引擎索引','Destination URL'=>'目标 URL','Canonical URL'=>'规范 URL','The canonical URL informs search crawlers which page is the main page if you have double content'=>'规范 URL 告诉搜索爬虫如果有重复内容，哪个页面是主页面','Breadcrumb Title'=>'面包屑标题','Breadcrumb Title to use for this post'=>'用于此文章的面包屑标题','Max Snippet'=>'最大摘要','Specify a maximum text-length, in characters, of a snippet for your page'=>'为您的页面指定摘要的最大文本长度（以字符为单位）','Max Video Preview'=>'最大视频预览','Specify a maximum duration in seconds of an animated video preview'=>'指定动画视频预览的最大持续时间（以秒为单位）','Max Image Preview'=>'最大图片预览','Specify a maximum size of image preview to be shown for images on this page'=>'指定此页面图像显示的图像预览最大尺寸','Show SEO Score on Front-end'=>'在前端显示 SEO 得分','Connect FREE Account'=>'连接免费帐户','By connecting your free account, you get keyword suggestions directly from Google when entering the focus keywords. Not only that, get access to our revolutionary Content AI, SEO Analyzer inside WordPress that scans your website for SEO errors and suggest improvements.'=>'通过连接您的免费帐户，在输入焦点关键词时直接从 Google 获取关键词建议。不仅如此，还可以访问我们革命性的 Content AI、WordPress 内部的 SEO 分析器，扫描您的网站以查找 SEO 错误并提出改进建议。','Read more by following this link.'=>'点击此链接阅读更多内容。','Enable Usage Tracking. %1$s Share anonymous usage data to help us improve Rank Math. No personal info is collected. %2$s'=>'启用使用情况跟踪。%1$s 分享匿名使用数据以帮助我们改进 Rank Math。不会收集任何个人信息。%2$s','Connect Your Account'=>'连接您的帐户','Skip Step'=>'跳过步骤','Take your SEO to the Next Level! '=>'将您的 SEO 提升到新水平！','Get Rank Math PRO! '=>'获取 Rank Math PRO！','Resetting…'=>'正在重置…','Resetted'=>'已重置','Updating…'=>'正在更新…','Updated'=>'已更新','Your sitemap index can be found here: '=>'您的网站地图索引可在此处找到：','Rank Math generates the default Sitemaps only and WPML takes care of the rest. When a search engine bot visits any post/page, it is shown hreflang tag that helps it crawl the translated pages. This is one of the recommended methods by Google. Please '=>'Rank Math 仅生成默认网站地图，WPML 负责其余部分。当搜索引擎机器人访问任何文章/页面时，会显示 hreflang 标签，帮助其爬取翻译后的页面。这是 Google 推荐的方法之一。请','Set the sitemap options for author archive pages.'=>'设置作者存档页面的网站地图选项。','Change Sitemap settings of %s.'=>'更改 %s 的网站地图设置。','Change Global meta settings that take effect across your website.'=>'更改影响整个网站的全局元设置。','Street Address'=>'街道地址','Locality'=>'地区','Region'=>'区域','Postal Code'=>'邮政编码','2-letter Country Code (ISO 3166-1)'=>'2 字母国家代码 (ISO 3166-1)','Add Number'=>'添加号码','Optimize for local searches and Knowledge Graph using these settings.'=>'使用这些设置优化本地搜索和知识图谱。','Add social account information to your website\'s Schema and Open Graph.'=>'向您网站的 Schema 和 Open Graph 添加社交帐户信息。','Static page is set as the front page (WP Dashboard > Settings > Reading). To add SEO title, description, and meta for the homepage, please click here: '=>'静态页面已设置为首页（WP 仪表盘 > 设置 > 阅读）。要为首页添加 SEO 标题、描述和元标记，请单击此处：','Add SEO meta and OpenGraph details to your homepage.'=>'向您的首页添加 SEO 元标记和 OpenGraph 详细信息。','Change SEO options related to the author archives.'=>'更改与作者存档相关的 SEO 选项。','Disable Date Archives'=>'禁用日期存档','Customize SEO meta settings of pages like search results, 404s, etc.'=>'自定义页面（如搜索结果、404 等）的 SEO 元设置。','Change Global SEO, Schema, and other settings for %s.'=>'更改 %s 的全局 SEO、Schema 和其他设置。','Add bulk editing columns to the terms listing screen.'=>'在术语列表屏幕中添加批量编辑列。','Save and Continue'=>'保存并继续','Return to dashboard'=>'返回仪表盘','Easy'=>'简单','For websites where you only want to change the basics and let Rank Math do most of the heavy lifting. Most settings are set to default as per industry best practices. One just has to set it and forget it.'=>'适用于只需要更改基本设置并让 Rank Math 完成大部分繁重工作的网站。大多数设置均按照行业最佳实践设置为默认值。只需设置一次即可高枕无忧。