 optimized replies for tweets to promote engagement and strengthen connections.'=>'生成优化的推文回复以促进参与并加强联系。','Instagram Caption'=>'Instagram 标题','Craft catchy captions for Instagram posts to increase engagement and grab attention.'=>'为 Instagram 帖子制作吸引人的标题，提高参与度并吸引注意力。','Create effective emails for promotions, announcements, and follow-ups to achieve marketing goals.'=>'创建有效的推广、公告和跟进邮件以实现营销目标。','Email Reply'=>'邮件回复','Craft courteous email replies to promote interaction and strengthen relationships.'=>'制作礼貌的邮件回复以促进互动并加强关系。','AIDA'=>'AIDA','Write persuasive text using the Attention-Interest-Desire-Action formula to drive action.'=>'使用注意-兴趣-欲望-行动公式编写有说服力的文本以推动行动。','IDCA'=>'IDCA','Create compelling messages using the Identify-Develop-Communicate-Ask strategy to resonate.'=>'使用识别-发展-沟通-询问策略创建引人入胜的信息以产生共鸣。','PAS'=>'PAS','Address customer problems with the Problem-Agitate-Solution technique to fulfill needs.'=>'使用问题-激化-解决方案技术解决客户问题以满足需求。','HERO'=>'HERO','Craft captivating headlines using the HERO formula to engage, reveal, and offer value.'=>'使用 HERO 公式制作吸引人的标题，以吸引、揭示和提供价值。','SPIN'=>'SPIN','Describe customer problems, highlight implications, and offer solutions using the SPIN method.'=>'使用 SPIN 方法描述客户问题，强调影响，并提供解决方案。','BAB'=>'BAB','Create a compelling Before-After-Bridge narrative to demonstrate product or service value.'=>'创建引人入胜的前后对比-桥梁叙述，以展示产品或服务价值。','YouTube Video Script'=>'YouTube 视频脚本','Develop engaging video scripts for YouTube to inform, entertain, and align.'=>'为 YouTube 开发引人入胜的视频脚本，以提供信息、娱乐和协调。','YouTube Video Description'=>'YouTube 视频描述','Generate informative and engaging video descriptions for YouTube.'=>'为 YouTube 生成信息丰富且引人入胜的视频描述。','Podcast Episode Outline'=>'播客节目大纲','Create detailed outlines for podcast episodes, including topics and takeaways.'=>'为播客节目创建详细大纲，包括主题和要点。','Create detailed and easy-to-follow recipes with ingredients, instructions, and nutrition.'=>'创建详细且易于遵循的食谱，包含食材、说明和营养信息。','Freeform Writing'=>'自由写作','Generate text based on prompts or topics, allo